var book = {
	"name": "Thu Hilhkikna",
	"numChapters": 34,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hihte pen Jordan galkhat gamlak, Suf galkhat Arabah gam sung, Paran le Tofel, Laban, Hazeroth le Dizahab kikalah Moses in Israel-te khempeuh tungah a gen thute ahi hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tua mun pen Horeb panin Seir Mual tawnin Kadeshbarnea lamah ni sawm le ni khat paina ahi hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Heshbon gamah a teng Amor kumpipa Sihon, le Ashtaroth le Edrei gamah a teng Bashan kumpipa a zawh khit ciangin, a kum sawmlina, kha sawm le kha khatna, a ni masa ni-in, amaute’ tungah thupiakna-in Topa in ama tungah a piak bangbangin Moses in Israel mite tungah a gen hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Moab gam Jordan galkhatah Moses in hih thu gentel a,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Horeb gam sungah Topa i Pasian in eite’ kiangah, ‘Hih mualah sauvei na om khinzo uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kithawi-in na khualzin uh kipan kik unla, Amor mite’ mualtung gam le Arabah kiim, mualtung gam, lei niamna gam, Negeb gam khempeuh, le Kanaan mite’ gam tuipi gei le Lebanon, gun golpi ahi Eufratis gun dongin pai un.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> En un, note’ mai-ah leitang ka koihzo hi. Pai unla, Topa in na pate uh Abraham, Isaac, Jakob, le amau’ nunga a suanlekhakte uh tungah piak dingin a ciam leitang luah un,’ hong ci hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Tua hun laitakin note kiangah, ‘Kei guak bek in note kong enzo kei ding hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Topa na Pasian un note tampi hong phasakzo hi. En un, note tuhunin vantung aksite zahin tampi na pha uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Topa, na pate uh Pasian in tu-a zah tulin note hong bawl hen la, note tungah hong ciamsa bangin thupha hong pia ta hen!",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kei guak in note’ thu kineihnate siansak nading tavuan lianpi bangci puakzawh ding ka hi hiam?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na minam uh tawh a kizui-in a pil, thuthei, thuphawksa mite teel unla, note’ lutangin amaute ka koih ding hi,’ kong ci hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Note in, ‘Nangma hong gen thu pen kote a dingin hoih hi,’ ci-in nong dawng uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tua ahih ciangin na minam lutang uh ahi, a pil thu phawksa mite ka la a, note’ tungah lutangin a tul uk, a za uk, a sawmnga uk, a sawm ukte, le uliante na minam khempeuh sung uhah ka koih hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Tua hun laitakin na thukhente uh ka thuhilh a, ‘Na sanggamte uh thu neihte za unla, mi khat le a sanggampa ahi a, amah tawh a om khualmipa tawh ahi zongin thu a mantakin khen un.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Thukhenna-ah angvan na nei kei ding uh hi. A neu le a liante a kibangin a thu na ngai ding uh a, maitang zahtak tuam na nei kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh thukhenna pen Pasian-a’ ahi hi. Note a dingin a haksa lua thute kei kiangah nong paipih ding uh a, keimah in tua thu ka za ding hi,’ ka ci hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Amaute’ hih ding na khempeuh tua hunin amaute kiangah thu ka pia hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Tua ciangin Horeb gam panin i ding khia a, Topa i Pasian in hong thupiak bangin Amor mite mualtung gam zuatna lamkalah note’ muhsa a lian a lauhuai sehnel gam i nawk khit ciangin Kadeshbarnea i tung hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tua ciangin note’ kiangah, ‘Topa i Pasian in eite hong piak Amor mite’ mualtung gam na tung khin uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> En un, Topa na Pasian un note’ mai-ah leitang koihzo hi. Topa, na pate uh Pasian in note tungah hong gensa bangin paito-in luah un. Lau kei unla, lungkia kei un,’ kong ci hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Tua ciangin na vekpi-un ka kiangah nong pai uh a, ‘Eite a dingin gam va enin, i paitoh nading lampi le i zuat ding khuapite hong genkik thei ding eite’ mai-ah mi sawl ni,’ nong ci uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Tua thu hoihtuak ka sa a, minam khatah khat, note mi sawm le nih kong la hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Amaute kithawi-in mualtung gamah paito uh a, Eshkol kuamah pai-in va en uh hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Amaute in tua gam singgah pawlkhat a khutun hong tawi-in i kiangah hong tunpihsuk uh a, amaute in eite kiangah thu hong zasakkikin, ‘Topa i Pasian in eite hong piak gam pen leitang hoih ahi hi,’ hong ci uh hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Ahi zongin note paito nuam loin, Topa na Pasian un hong thupiak na nial uh hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na puanbukte uh sungah na phun uh a, ‘Topa in eite hong mudah ahih manin eite a hong susia ding Amor mite’ khut sungah hong pia dingin Egypt gam panin eite hong paikhiatpih hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Koi lai-ah paito ding ihi hiam? I sanggamte in i lungsim hong siasak khin uh a, “A mite ei sangin lianzaw-in sangzaw uh hi. A khuapite lianin van banin ki-um hi. Tua tham loin Anak mite tua munah ka mu uh hi,” hong ci uh hi,’ na ci uh hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Tua ciangin note kiangah, ‘Lau kei unla, amaute kihta kei un.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Egypt gam sungah note’ mit muhah a hih bangin, mi khat in a tapa a puak bangin hih mun na tun matengun lam tawntung ah Topa na Pasian un note hong puak na muhsa uh sehnel gam a mah bangin, note’ mai-ah a pai Topa na Pasian un note a dingin hong dosak ding hi,’ kong ci hi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ahi zongin hih bang thu om hinapi-in, na puanbuk lamna mun ding uh hong lak ding le na pai nading lampi uh hong lak dingin zanin mei, sunin meii tawh note’ mai lampi-ah a pai Topa na Pasian uh note in na um kei uh hi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Topa in note’ thu hong za a, a heh suakin kiciam a,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ‘Hih a gi lo khang mite khat beek in, na pate uh tungah piak dinga ka ciam gam hoih na mu kei ding uh a, Jefunneh’ tapa Kaleb bek in tua gam mu ding hi. Amah in a lungsim khempeuh tawh Topa zui ahih manin amah le a tate tungah ama totsa leitang ka pia ding hi!’ a ci hi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Note’ hangin kei tungah zong Topa heh a, ‘Nang zong tua gamah na pai kei ding hi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Nun’ tapa Joshua, nangma mai-ah a ding pa lut ding hi. Amah hanthawn in; bang hang hiam cih leh amah in Israel mite tua gam luahsak ding hi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> “Tua tham loin galte’ mat suak ding hi, na cih uh na taneute uh le, tuhun laitakin a sia le a pha a khenthei nai lo na tate uh, tua gamah pai ding a, amaute tungah tua gam pia-in, amaute in tua gam luah ding uh hi.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ahih hangin note ahihleh, kihei unla, San Tuipi lam manawhin sehnel gamah pai un,’ hong ci hi.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> “Tua ciangin note in kei nong dawng uh a, ‘Topa’ tungah ka khial khin uh hi. Topa i Pasian in hong thupiak bang teekteekin paito-in i do ding hi,’ nong ci uh hi. Na milipun na galhiam uh tawh na kithawi uh a, mualtung gamah paitoh ding na baih ngaihsut uh hi.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> “Tua ciangin Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Amaute kiangah gen in: Note lakah kei om lo ka hih manin kuanto kei unla, do kei un. Tua bangin kuanto le-uhcin na galte uh na lel ding uh hi, ci in,’ hong ci hi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Tua ahih ciangin note kiangah kong gen a, note in na ngai nuam kei uh hi. Topa’ thupiakna na nial uh a, mualtung gamah na kuanto hamtang uh hi.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Tua ciangin tua mualtung gamah a teng Amor mite hong kuanin, Seir gam Hormah ciang dongah khuai bangin hong delhin hong zo uh hi.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Note hong ciahkikin Topa’ mai-ah na kap uh hi. Ahih hangin Topa in na aw uh hong ngai loin, a bil zong hong ngat lo hi.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Tua ahih ciangin tua thu hangin ni tampi sung Kadesh munah na om uh hi."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Tua ciangin Topa in kei tungah hong gen bangin eite kihei-in San Tuipi lam manawhin sehnel gamah i pai a, ni tampi sung Seir Mual tung gamah i pai kawikawi hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Tua ciangin Topa in kei tungah,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ‘Hih mual kiimah sauvei khop na pai khinta uh hi; leilu lamah kihei un.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mite’ tungah hih bangin thu pia in: Seir gamah a teng Esau’ suanlekhak, na behte uh gam sung a nawk ding na hi uh hi. Amaute in note hong kihta ding uh hi. Ahi zongin note kidawm un.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Amaute tawh kisel kei un; bang hang hiam cih leh amau’ leitang themkhat zong no kong pia peuhmah kei ding hi. Esau’ neih dingin ama tungah Seir Mual pia khin ka hih manin khe a ta khopzah zong no kong pia kei ding hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na nek ding uh an amaute’ tung panin sum tawh na lei ding uh a, na dawn ding uh amau’ tui zong sum mah tawh na lei ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “‘Bang hang hiam cih leh na sepna khempeuh uhah Topa na Pasian un note thupha hong pia hi. Hih a zai sehnel gam na paina uh amah in hong thei hi. Hih kum sawmli sung Topa na Pasian uh no tawh hong om hi. Bangmah na kisam kei uh hi, ci-in gen in,’ hong ci hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin Seir gamah a teng Esau’ suan i behte, le Elath le Eziongeber khua pan hong kipan Arabah lampi panin i paikhia suak hi. “Tua ciangin eite kihei-in Moab gam lamah i pai hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Amau’ leitang na neih dingun note’ tungah hong pia lo ding ka hih manin Moab mite gimsak kei unla, amaute tawh galin kido kei un; bang hang hiam cih leh a neih dingun Lot’ suanlekhakte tungah Ar khua ka piazo hi,’ hong ci hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> (Anak mite zahin a tun a sang, a lian, a tam Emim mite tua lai-ah teng ngei hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Anak mite mah bangin amaute zong Refaim mite kici a, ahih hangin Moab mite in Emim ci uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hor mite zong Seir-ah nidangin teng ngei a, ahih hangin Topa in amaute’ tungah a piak amau’ leitang tungah Israel mite in a hih mah bangin, Esau’ suanlekhakte in amaute suankhia-in susia uh a, amau’ munah teng uh hi.)",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Tua ciangin Topa in, ‘Tu-in ding unla Zered lui kantan un,’ hong cih bangin Zered lui i kantan hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Amaute tungah Topa a kiciam mah bangin galsim mi ahi tua khangmite khempeuh gam sungah a sih khit dong ahi, Kadeshbarnea i nusiat a kipan Zered lui i kantan dong kikal kum sawmthum le kum giat ahi hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Amaute a bei khit mateng gamlakah amaute a susia dingin Topa langpang takpi hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin mihingte lak panin galsim mite bei-in a sih khit ciangin",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Topa in kei kiangah,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ‘Tuni-in Ar khua san takah Moab gamgi a kantan ding na hi uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ammon mite’ leitang na neih dingun khat zong hong pia lo ding ka hih manin, Ammon mite’ gamgi na nai uh ciangin amaute gimsak kei unla, amaute tawh kido kei un; bang hang hiam cih leh a neih dingun Lot’ suanlekhakte tungah ka pia khin hi,’ hong ci hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> (Tua pen Refaim gamgi ci-in zong kithei ngei hi. Refaim mite tua lai-ah teng ngei a, ahih hangin Ammon mite in amaute pen, Anak mite bangin lianin a tun a sang ahi Zamzummim mite ci uh hi. Ahih hangin Topa in amaute’ mai-ah tua mite susia hi. Amaute in tua mite suankhia uh a, amau’ munah teng uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Amah in Seir-ah a teng Esau’ suanlekhakte a dingin amaute’ mai-ah Hor mite a suksiat mah bangin amaute in tua mite susia-in tuni dongin amau’ munah teng uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Gaza ciang dong khuaneute-ah a teng Avvim mite ahihleh Kaftor pana hong pai Kaftor mite in susia-in amau’ munah teng uh hi.)",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Moab gam sung i khen’ ciangin Topa in, ‘Ding un, na khualzin uh kipan unla, Arnon kuam kantan un. En un, Heshbon kumpipa, Amor mi Sihon le ama leitang note’ khut sungah kong piazo hi. Amah suankhiat ding kipan unla, gal sungah amah tawh kido un.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nomau’ thu za-in note’ hangin lingin a gim ding ahi, mun khempeuhah a om mite’ tungah note hong kikihtakna le note’ hanga launa ka tunsak ding tuni-in ka kipan ding hi,’ hong ci hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin Kedemoth sehnel gam panin Heshbon kumpipa Sihon’ kiangah kilemna ding thu genin kamtai ka sawl a,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ‘Na gam sung hong nawksak in. Lampi bekah ka pai ding uh a, taklam ahi a, veilamah ahi zongin ka pial kei ding uh hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ka nek ding uh an sum tawh lei dingin nong zuak ding a, ka dawn ding uh tui sum tawh lei dingin nong pia ding hi. Khe tawh hong nawksak bek in.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Jordan kantanin Topa ka Pasian un kote hong piak leitangah ka tun matengun Seir-a a teng Esau’ suante le Ar-a a teng Moab mite in kei hong paisak mah bangun hong paisak in,’ ka ci hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> “Ahih hangin Heshbon kumpipa Sihon in eite hong paisak lo hi; bang hang hiam cih leh tuhuna mah bangin na khutsung uhah amah hong piak theih nadingin Topa na Pasian un a lungsim khauhsakin, amah paupeengsak hi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Tua ciangin Topa in kei kiangah, ‘En in, Sihon le a leitang nang tungah piak kong kipan khinzo hi. Ama leitang na luah theih nadingin suankhiat kipan in,’ hong ci hi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Tua ciangin Sihon le a mite khempeuh eite a do dingin Jahaz-ah hong pai uh hi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Topa i Pasian in amah hong pia a, amah le a tapate le a mi khempeuh i zo hi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Tua hunin a khuapi khempeuh i la a, a khuapi khempeuh, papi, nupi, le naupangte i susia maimang a, bangmah i siit kei hi.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> I laksa a khuapi sunga van kinusiate tawh a ganhingte uh eima a dingin i la bek hi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Arnon kuam mong a a om Aroer le tua kuam sunga om khuapi Gilead ciang dongah eite a dingin khuapikulh a sanglua khat beek om lo a, Topa i Pasian in a vekpi-in eite’ khut sungah hong pia hi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ammon mite’ leitang ahi Jabbok gun pang khempeuh le mualtung gam khuapite le Topa eite’ Pasian in hong khamna munte bek i va neh kei hi."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Tua ciangin eite kihei-in Bashan lamah i paito a, Bashan kumpipa Og le ama mite khempeuh Edrei-ah eite a do dingin hong kuankhia hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ahih hangin Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Amah kihta kei in; bang hang hiam cih leh amah le a mite khempeuh le a leitang nangma khut sungah kong pia khinzo hi. Heshbon-ah a teng Amor kumpipa Sihon na bawl bangin ama tungah na bawl ding hi,’ hong ci hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin Topa i Pasian in eite’ khut sungah Bashan kumpipa Og le a mite khempeuh zong hong pia a, ama a dingin mi khat beek a suakta nawn lo dingin i vatmai hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tua hunin a khuapite khempeuh uh i la a, amau’ kiang pan i lak loh khuapi khat zong om lo hi. Tua banga i lakte pen Bashan gam a Og kumpi gam sung, Argob gambup, khuapi sawmgukte ahi hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kulhpi-a ki-um lo khuaneu tampite simloh, hih khuapite khempeuh kulh sangpi, kongpi le sikzawlte tawh a muanhuai takin a kibawl ahi hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Heshbon kumpipa Sihon i bawl bangin amaute i susiamang a, a khuapi khempeuh, papi, nupi, le naupangte i susia hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ahih hangin a ganhing khempeuh le khuapi sunga van kinusiate i la hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin tua hun laitakin, Jordan galkhat a om Amor kumpi nihte’ khutsung pan, Arnon kuam panin Hermon Mual dong",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> (Sidon mite in Hermon pen Sirion ci a, Amor mite in Senir ci uh hi),",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> mualzang khuapite khempeuh le Gilead gam khempeuh le Bashan gam khempeuh, Salekah le Edrei dong, Bashan-a om Og kumpi gam khuapite i la hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> (Bang hang hiam cih leh Bashan kumpipa Og bek Refaim gam sungah a omlai ahi hi. Ama lupna a han pen suang han hi a, Ammon mite’ khuapi Rabbah-ah tua han omlai hi lo ahi hiam? Tua han a sauna pi sawm le li dektak hi a, a zaina pi guk ahi hi.)",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Tua hunin hih leitang i luah ciangin, Reuben mite le Gad mite tungah Arnon kuam mong a a om Aroer pan le Gilead mualtung gam kimkhat a khuapite tawh ka pia hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Gilead gam a omlai teng le Argob gam khempeuh ahi, Og kumpi gam, Bashan gam khempeuh, Manasseh minam kimkhatte tungah ka pia hi. (Bashan gam buppi pen Refaim leitang kici hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Manasseh mi Jair in Bashan kici Argob gam khempeuh, Geshur mite le Maakath mite’ gamgi dong la a, tua sunga khuaneu minte ama min tamsakin tuni donga a kip Havvothjair a phuak hi.)",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Makhir tungah Gilead ka pia a,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Reuben mite le Gad mite tungah Gilead panin Arnon kuam dong, gamgi dingin a kuam laita, Ammon mite’ gamgi ahi Jabbok gun dong tawh ka pia hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Arabah gam zong, a gamgi dingin Jordan tawh, Khinnereth pan nisuahna lama om Pisgah mualpang nuai-a Ci Tuipi ahi Arabah tuipi ciang dong amaute ka pia hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Tua hunin note thu kong pia a, ‘Topa na Pasian un na neih dingun hih leitang hong piazo hi. Na galhang mite khempeuh uh galhiam tawh kithawi-in Israel mi na sanggamte uh mai-ah va kuan ding hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ahih hangin na zite, na taneute, le na ganhingte uh (ganhing tampi na neih uh ka thei hi) note kong piaksa khuapite-ah om ding uh a,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Topa in note hong piak bangin na sanggamte uh tungah lungsim tawlngakna pia-in, Topa na Pasian un Jordan galkhatah amaute a piak leitang amaute in zong a luah matengun na huh ding uh hi. Tua ciangin note kong piaksa ahi na neihsa ciat uhah note khempeuh na ciah ding uh hi,’ kong ci hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Tua hun laitakin Joshua thu ka pia a, ‘Topa na Pasian in hih kumpi nihte’ tungah a bawlte khempeuh na mit in mu khin a, na nawk lai ding kumpi gam khempeuh tungah zong Topa in tua mah bangin hih ding hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Amaute na kihta kei ding hi; bang hang hiam cih leh nang a’ dinga hong dosak pa pen Topa na Pasian ahi hi,’ ka ci hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Tua hunin keimah in Topa’ tungah ka thum a,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ‘Topa Pasian aw, na liatna le na thahatnate na nasempa’ tungah lah ding a hong kipan pan bek na hi hi; bang hang hiam cih leh vantung hitaleh leitungah hitaleh nangma hih bangin tua bang nasep leh a vanglian gamtatna a hih thei bang pasian om ahi hiam?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kei hong paisak inla, Jordan galkhat a om gam hoih, tua mualtung gam hoih le Lebanon hong musak in, ci-in kong thum hi,’ ka ci hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Ahih hangin note’ hangin kei’ tungah Topa heh a, ka thunget hong pia lo hi. Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Phazo hi; hih thu kei kiangah hong gen nawn kei in.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Pisgah mual dawnah paito inla, nitumna lam, leilu lam, leitaw lam, le nisuahna lamah khuadakto inla, na mit tawh gal et in; bang hang hiam cih leh nangmah in hih Jordan na kantan kei ding hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ahih hangin Joshua thu pia inla, hanthawnin thakhauhsak in; bang hang hiam cih leh hih mite’ mai-ah amah pai ding a, nangmah in na muh ding leitang amaute luahsak ding hi,’ hong ci hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin Bethpeor gal-a kuam sungah i taam lai hi."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Tu-in Israel-te aw, note nungta-in, Topa, na pate uh Pasian in note hong piak leitangah va pai-in na luah theih nadingun note kong hilh thukhamte le ngeina kipte don unla zui un.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Topa na Pasian un hong piak ahi keima hong thugente na zuih theih nadingun no kong thupiakte behlap loin, zong na khiam kei ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na mit un Baalpeor-ah Topa’ hihna mu khin hi; bang hang hiam cih leh na Pasian un note’ lak panin Peor-a Baal a zui mi khempeuh susia a,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ahih hangin Topa na Pasian uh a lenkipte khempeuh tuni-in na hinglai uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “En un, note in a luah dingin na lutna uh gam sungah na zuih dingun Topa ka Pasian in kei hong thupiak bangin thukhamte le ngeina kipte kong hilh khinzo hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tuate zui unla, sem un; bang hang hiam cih leh hih thukhamte khempeuh a zak uh ciangin, ‘Hih minam liante pen a pil thuthei taktak hi,’ a ci ding uh mite’ muhna-ah hih thu pen nomau’ pilna le nomau’ theihna hi ding hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Bang hang hiam cih leh eite in Topa i sap hun simin eite’ kiangah i Pasian hong nai zahin tua bang pasian a nei minam lian koi-ah om ahi hiam?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tuni-in note kong hilh thute bangin thukham le ngeina kip a man a nei minam lian koi-ah om ahi hiam?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Na mit un a muhsa nate na nuntak sungun mangngilh kha-in, na lungsim panun paikhia kha ding ahih manin limtakin ngaihsunin hoihtakin kikem un. Horeb-a Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah na din ni-un Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Leitungah a nuntak laiteng uh amaute in kei hong kihtakna ding le amaute in a tate uh a hilhsawn theih nadingun keimah in amaute tungah ka thute ka zaksak theih nadingin ka kiangah mite hong khawm in,’ hong cihna thu, na tate uh le na tate uh tate’ tungah kitheisak un.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Mei in mual kangin van laizang dong banto-in, khuamial le meii le khuazing in a tuamcip laitakin note a nai-ah hong pai-in mual bulah na ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tua ciangin mei sung panin Topa in note’ kiangah thu hong gen hi. Note in awging na za uh a, ahih hangin bangmah mu loin, awging bek a om hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Thupiak Sawmte ahi note’ hih dinga hong thupiak ama thuciamna note’ tungah hong gen a, amah in suangpek nih tungah tuate a gelh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Note in na luah ding uh gam sungah na zuih theih nadingun, thukhamte le ngeina kipte note kong hilhna ding tua hun laitakin Topa in kei thu hong pia hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin note hoihtakin kidawm un. Horeb-ah mei sung panin Topa in note’ tungah thu hong gen ni-in bangmah mu lo na hih manun,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> note a dingin lim khat peuhpeuh, pasal tawh a kibang hitaleh numei tawh a kibang hitaleh,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> leitung a om ganhing khat peuhpeuh tawh a kibang hitaleh, huihlaka leeng kha a nei vasa khat peuhpeuh tawh a kibang hitaleh,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> leitungah a bokvak khat peuhpeuh tawh a kibang hitaleh, leinuai-ah a om tui sunga ngasa khat peuhpeuh tawh a kibang hitaleh, a kiseek milim bawlna tawh a sia-in na gamtat khak loh nadingun kidawm un.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Note in na mit uh tawh vantung lam ento-in, ni le kha le aksite, vantung na khempeuh na muh uh ciangin, mun khempeuh a mite’ tungah Topa na Pasian un a piak nate’ lamah kihei-in tuate bia-in a na na sep khak loh nading uh kidawm un.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ahih hangin Topa in tuni-a bangin sik meikhuk tawh a kibang Egypt panin ama neih mi dingin note hong la-in hong paikhiatpih khin hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tua tham loin note’ hangin kei’ tungah Topa heh a, keimah in Jordan kantan loin Topa na Pasian un note’ gamh dingin hong piak leitang hoihah ka lut loh nadingin a kiciam hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hih gamah kei ka si ding a, Jordan khengin ka pai thei kei ding hi. Ahih hangin note in kantanin tua gam hoih na luah ding uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Topa na Pasian un note tawh hong bawl thuciamna mangngilhin, Topa na Pasian un note’ hih dinga hong kham lim khat peuhpeuh tawh a kibang a kiseek milim na bawlkhak loh nadingun kidawm un.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian uh hong kangtum thei mei tawh kibang a, a haza Pasian ahi hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Note in tuleta nei-in gam sungah mi khangham na suah uh ciangin, na khat peuhpeuh tawh a kibang limin a kiseek milim bawlna le Topa na Pasian uh’ muhna-ah a sia bawlna tawh amah a heh nadingin na siat gamtat uhleh,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Jordan galkhat luah dingin na paina leitang uhah na siat maimang baih nadingun note’ langkhatah teci pang dingin tuni-in van le lei ka sam hi. Tua leitang tungah note sauvei na hing kei ding uh a, na siamaimang ding uh hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Topa in mite lakah note hong thehthang ding a, Topa in note hong hawlna minamte lakah mi tawmcik bek na omlai ding uh hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Note in tua lai munah mite’ khut in a bawl, khua mu thei lo, khua za thei lo, a ne thei lo, a nam thei lo sing le suang pasian-te’ na na sem ding uh hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ahih hangin tua lai panin Topa na Pasian uh na zong ding uh a, na lungsim khempeuh uh le na nuntakna khempeuh uh tawh na zon uhleh amah na mu ding uh hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Note in gimna thuakin, mailam hunah hih nate khempeuh note’ tungah hong tun ciangin, Topa na Pasian uh lamah kihei-in ama thu na mang ding uh hi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian uh hehpihna a nei Pasian ahi hi. Amah in note hong tamasak loin, hong nusia lo ding a, na pate uh tawh a thuciamna mangngilh lo ding hi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Pasian in leitungah mi a piansak ni a kipan, note’ pian’ ma-a hun beisa thu tu-in kan unla, van mong khat pan mong khat kikal thu zong kan un. Hih bang na lian piang ngei-in, a kiza ngei peuhmah hiam?",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Note in Pasian’ aw za khin napi-in na hin lai uh bangin meikuang sung panin pasian dang khat peuhpeuh’ pauna aw mi khat peuhpeuh in za ngei ahi hiam?",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Tua ahih kei leh, Topa na Pasian un Egypt gam sungah note a dingin na muhna uhah a bawlte khempeuh tawh a kibangin, ze-etna, lim, nalamdang, gal, a vanglian le a thahatna le a lauhuai mahmah tawh pasian dang khat peuhpeuh in ama mite a dingin minamdang khat sung pan minam khat a va lak ding hanciam ngam ngei ahi hiam?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Topa Pasian hi, ci-in na theih nadingun note’ tungah hih thu hong kilak hi a, amah simloh kuamah dang om lo hi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Amah in note hong khal theih nadingin vantung panin ama aw note hong zasak hi. A mei lianpi leitungah note hong musak a, mei sung panin ama aw na za uh hi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Amah in na pate uh itin, amau’ suanlekhakte hong teel a, amahmah in ama vanglian tawh Egypt panin note hong paikhiatpih a,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> note sangin a tamzaw le a vanglian zawte’ gamah hong paipihin, note’ luah dingin amau’ leitang hong piak nadingin note’ mai-ah amaute hong hawlkhiatsak ahih manin tuni-in hih bangin na om thei uh hi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Tua ahih ciangin tunga om vantung hitaleh nuai-a om leitung hitaleh ah Topa pen Pasian ahihna thu tuni-in thei unla, na lungsim uhah ciamteh un; kuamah dang om lo hi.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Tua ahih ciangin note le note’ khita na tate uh tungah thu hong nuamin, Topa na Pasian un a tawntung a hong piak gam sungah na khan uh na sausak theih nadingun tuni-a no kiangah kong gen ahi ama thukhamte le a thupiakte na zui ding uh hi,” a ci hi.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Tua ciangin, a beisa hunah amah tawh kilangneihna a om lo, tum lopi-in a vengpa a that, mi that khapa va tai-in, hih khuapite khat peuhpeuhah taina tawh a suahtak theih nadingin Moses in nisuahna lam Jordan galkhatah khuapi thum a tuam koih hi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Reuben mite a dingin mualzang sehnel gam Beza khua, Gad mite a dingin Gilead gam sung Ramoth khua, le Manasseh mite a dingin Bashan gam sung Golan khua ahi hi.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Moses in Israel mite tungah thu pia hi.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Hihte pen, Egypt gam panin a paikhiat-un Moses le Israel mite in a zawh Heshbon-ah a teng Amor mite’ kumpipa Sihon’ gam sung, Jordan gal, Bethpeor tawh a kigalsai kuam sungah, Egypt panin Israel mite a paikhiat lai-in Moses in amaute tungah a gen thute ahi hi.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Amaute in, Arnon kuam mong a a om Aroer panin Sirion Mual (Hermon a cihna) dong, Jordan nisuahna lama om Arabah gam khempeuh, Pisgah mualpang nuai Arabah tuipi dong tawh, kumpi Sihon’ leitang le Bashan kumpi Og’ leitang, Jordan galkhat nisuahna lamah a teng Amor kumpi nihte’ leitang a luah uh hi."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Moses in Israel-te khempeuh samin amaute kiangah, “Israel-te aw, tuni-a note’ zakin kong gen thukhamte le ngeina kipte ngai unla, note in thei-in limtakin zuih ding na ngaihsun ding uh hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Topa i Pasian in eite tawh Horeb-ah thuciamna khat bawl hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Topa in i pute i pate bek tawh hih thuciamna a bawl hi loin, tuni-a a hinglai eite khempeuh tawh zong a bawl ahi hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Note’ tungah Topa’ thu a gen dingin Topa le note’ kikalah ka din laitakin, mei sung panin tua mualah Topa in kimaituahin note hong hopih a, mei hangin note lau na hih manun mualtungah na paito kei uh hi. Amah in:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “‘Kei pen salsuahna Egypt leitang panin note a hong paikhiatpih Topa na Pasian uh ka hi hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “‘Keimah longal pasian dang na nei kei ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “‘A kiseek milim hitaleh, tunga vantung hitaleh, nuai-a leitung hitaleh, leinuai-a om tui sung hitaleh ah a om na khat peuhpeuh a sun khat peuhpeuh note a dingin na bawl kei ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Amaute’ mai-ah kun loin, amau’ na na sem kei ding uh hi; bang hang hiam cih leh keimah Topa note’ Pasian, a aam Pasian ka hi a, kei hong mudahte’ tungah a pate’ mawhna a tate’ tungah khang thum khang lina dongin thuk-in,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ahih hangin kei hong itin ka thupiakte a zui mi a tul tampite’ tungah itna kip a lak pa ka hi hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Topa note’ Pasian’ min a sia lamin na zang kei ding uh hi; bang hang hiam cih leh Topa in ama min a sia lamin a zang mi a mawh lo hi, ci lo ding hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “‘Topa note’ Pasian in hong thupiak bangin na sianthosak nadingun Sabbath ni tang un.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ni guk sung na semin na nasep ding khempeuh uh na hih ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ahih hangin a ni sagih ni pen Topa note’ Pasian’ Sabbath ni ahi hi. Tua ni-in note bangin na nasem numei le na nasem pasalte uh a tawlngak theih nadingin note, na tapate, na tanute, na nasemnute, na nasempate, na bawngtal, na la, na ganhing khat peuhpeuh uh le na huang sung uha om zinte in na khat peuhpeuh sem lo ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Egypt-ah nasem na hihna uh le tua lai panin Topa na Pasian un a vangliatna khut le a thahatna tawh hong paikhiatpihna na phawk ding uh hi. Tua ahih ciangin Sabbath ni na tan’ ding uh Topa note’ Pasian in thu hong pia hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “‘Topa note’ Pasian in hong piak leitang tungah na khan uh sau-in na nopsak theih nadingun Topa note’ Pasian in hong thupiak bangin na nu na pa uh zahtak un.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “‘Mi na that kei ding uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “‘Nulepa mawhna zong na bawl kei ding uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “‘Na na gu kei ding uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “‘Na vengte uh langkhatah zong a man loin teci na pang kei ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “‘Na vengte uh zi zong na deihgawh kei ding uh hi. Na vengte’ inn, a lo, a nasempa, a nasemnu, a bawngtal, a la, ahih kei leh na vengte’ na khat peuhpeuh na deihgawh kei ding uh hi,’ ci hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Topa in mei, meii, le a mial mahmah sung panin awging lianpi tawh mualtung a no a kikhawm khempeuh tungah hih thute hong gen a, amah in bangmah dang genthuah lo hi. Amah in suangpek nih tungah tuate gelhin, tua suangpeekte kei tungah hong pia hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Mei in mual a kat laitakin khuamial sung panin awging na zak uh ciangin minam lutang khempeuh le upate kei kiangah hong pai uh hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Note in, ‘En in, Topa i Pasian in a minthanna le a liatna eite’ tungah hong lak khin a, mei sung panin ama awging i za khin hi. Pasian in mi hopih napi, mi a hinglai veve-in tuni-in i mu hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Tua ahih ciangin bang hangin tu-in eite si ding ihi hiam? Hih mei lianpi in eite hong kangtum ding hi. Topa i Pasian’ awging za lai lehang eite i si ding hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh a si thei mihing khempeuh sung panin eite’ zak bangin mei sung panin a nungta Pasian a paukhiatna awging za-in a nungta lai kua om ahi hiam?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> A nai-ah va pai inla, Topa i Pasian in a gen ding khempeuh va za in. Topa i Pasian in nang tungah hong genteng ko’ tungah nang hong gensawn in. Kote in hong mangin ka sem ding uh hi,’ nong ci uh hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Kei kiangah nong gen uh ciangin Topa in na thu uh a za hi. Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Hih mite in nang kiangah hong gen uh thu ka za khin a, a gen khempeuh uh a manin gen uh hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Amaute le a suan a khakte uh a nopsak tawntung theih nadingun keimah zahtak ding le ka thupiak khempeuh zuih ding hih bang ngaihsutna nei tawntung le-uh ka deih ahi hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Pai inla amaute kiangah, “Na puanbuk uhah ciah un,” ci in.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ahih hangin nang, kei kiang hih lai-ah ding in. Amaute’ neih dingin ka piak leitangah amaute in a zuih theih nadingun amaute na hilh ding thupiakna le thukhamte le ngeina kipte khempeuh nang tungah kong gen ding hi,’ hong ci hi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin Topa na Pasian un note hong thupiak bangin na gamtat ding uh na kingaihsun ding uh a, ama thu panin taklam hitaleh veilam hitaleh ah na pial kei ding uh hi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Note nungta-in, nuamsa-in na luah ding uh leitangah sawtpi na nuntak nadingun Topa na Pasian un note hong thupiakna lampi khempeuh na tawn ding uh hi."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Tu-in, luah dinga na paina gam uhah na zuih dingun, note le na tapate uh le na suanlekhakte un Topa note’ Pasian’ thukhamte le a thupiakte na zuihna uh tawh amah na zahtak theih nadingun, Topa na Pasian un na nuntak tawntung uh na zuih dingun kei a hong hilh sawnsak thute pen hih thupiakna, thukhamte, le ngeina kipte ahi hi. Hihte pen na khan uh a sau theih nading ahi hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tua ahih ciangin Israel-te aw, note nuamsa-in, Topa, na pate uh Pasian in note tungah hong ciamsa bangin bawngnawi le khuaizu a luanna gamah tampi pha-in na khan theih nadingun hih thute za unla, na zuih ding uh ngaihsun un.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Israel-te aw, za un: Topa i Pasian, Topa khat bek ahi hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Topa note’ Pasian, na lungsim khempeuh uh, na nuntakna khempeuh uh, le na thahatna khempeuh uh tawh na it ding uh hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tuni-a no kong piak hih thute na lungsim uhah om ding hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na tate uh tungah limtakin na hilh ding uh a, na innsung uhah na tut uh ciang, lampi-ah na pai uh ciang, na lup ciang uh le na thawh ciangun tua thute na gengen ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na khut tung uhah lim dingin tuate na hen ding uh a, na mitte uh kikalah tuate pen talsuante bang hi ding hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na inn kongkhak khuam tung uh le na kongpi uh tungah tuate na gelh ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Topa na Pasian un note piak dingin na pate uh Abraham, Isaac, le Jakob tungah a ciam, note’ phuh loh a lian a hoih khuapite,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> note’ khol loh na hoih khempeuh tawh a kidim innte, note’ bawl loh tuibeem, note’ suan loh leengguite, le oliv kungte a omna leitangah hong paipihin, note in ne-in na kham uh ciangin,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> salsuahna Egypt leitang panin hong paikhiatpih Topa na mangngilh khak loh nading uh kidawm un.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Topa na Pasian uh na zahtak ding uh hi. Ama na bek na sem ding uh a, ama min tawh na kiciam ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Note’ kiima om mite’ pasian-te ahi pasian dangte’ nung na zui kei ding uh hi;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bang hang hiam cih leh note’ lakah a om Topa na Pasian uh a aam Pasian ahi hi. Tua bang hikeileh note’ tungah Topa na Pasian uh hong hehin, lei maitang panin note hong susia ding hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Massah munah amah na ze-et uh bangin Topa na Pasian uh na ze-et nawn kei ding uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Amah in note hong thupiaksa ahi Topa na Pasian un hong thupiakte khempeuh na zui ding uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Topa’ hong ciamsa bangin note’ mai panin na langte khempeuh uh nawhkhiatna tawh na pu na pate uh tungah piak dingin Topa in a ciamsa leitang hoih note in na luah theih nading uh le note na nopsak theih nadingun Topa’ muhna-ah a man le a hoih nate na sem ding uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Hong tung ding hunah na tapate un, ‘Topa i Pasian in note hong piak hih thute, bang a cihnopna ahi hiam?’ ci-in hong dot uh ciangin",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na tapate uh kiangah, ‘Eite pen Egypt gam sungah Faro’ silate ihi a, Topa in Egypt panin a vangliatna tawh hong paikhiatpih hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Topa in eite’ muhna-ah a lian a nasia lim le na lamdangte Egypt mite le Faro le a uliante khempeuh tungah lak hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Amah in i pu i pate tungah piak dinga a ciam leitangah hong paipihin, eite hong piak theih nadingin tua lai panin eite hong paikhiatpih hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tuhuna bangin i nuntak theih nadingin amah in eite’ hoih tawntung ding a deihna-in, Topa i Pasian zahtakin hih thukhamte khempeuh i zuih ding Topa in thu hong pia hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Amah in eite hong thupiak bangin Topa i Pasian’ mai-ah hih thupiakte khempeuh limtakin zui lehang eite a dingin thumanna hi ding hi,’ na ci ding uh hi."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Topa na Pasian un luah dinga na tumna uh leitangah hong paipihin, note’ mai-ah Hit mite, Girgash mite, Amor mite, Kanaan mite, Perez mite, Hiv mite, le Jebus mite, note sangin lianzaw-in a thahatzaw minam sagihte note’ mai panin siangkhiasakin,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Topa na Pasian un note tungah amaute hong pia-in, note in amaute na zawh uh ciangin, note in amaute na susiamang ding uh hi. Amaute tawh thuciamna na bawl kei ding uh a, amaute tungah hehpihna na lak kei ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Amaute tawh kiteng loin, na tanute uh amau’ tapate pia loin, a tanute uh na tapate uh a dingin na la kei ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh pasian dangte’ na a sem dingin Topa zuihna panin na tapate uh amaute in heikhia ding uh hi. Tua ciangin no tungah Topa hong hehin note hong susia pak ding hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Amaute tungah hih bangin note na gamta ding uh hi: A biakna taute uh phelsakin, a biakna songte uh dengzanin, amau’ Asherah milimte phuksakin, a kiseek a milimte uh mei tawh na hal ding uh hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Bang hang hiam cih leh note pen Topa note’ Pasian’ tungah a siangtho mi na hi uh hi. Leitung a om mite khempeuh sung panin ama mi ahi dingin Topa na Pasian un note hong teelzo hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Topa in note hong itin hong teelna pen midangte sangin na tamzawkna hang uh hi lo hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh mi khempeuh lakah a tawmpen na hi uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Topa in salsuahna Egypt kumpipa Faro’ khutsung panin note hong honkhia-in a vangliatna tawh hong paikhiatpihna pen Topa in note hong itin, na pate uh tunga a kiciam thuciam a zuihna hang ahi hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tua ahih ciangin Topa na Pasian uh amah bek ahi Pasian hi a, amah itin a thupiakna a zuite tungah khang tulkhat dongin thuciamna le itna kip lenin a thuman Pasian,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> amah a mudah mite, suksiatna tawh a thukpah pa ahihna thei un. Amah a mudah mi tungah zekai loin a maitang mahah thuk ding hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tua ahih ciangin tuni-a no kong piak thute khempeuh limtakin na zuih ding uh ngaihsun un.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Note in hih ngeina kipte za-in, kemin tuate na zuihna hangun, Topa na Pasian un na pu na pate uh tungah a ciam thuciamna le itna kip note tungah hong tungsak ding hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Amah in note hong itin, tampi hong phasak ding hi. Amah in note tungah piak dingin na pu na pate uh tungah a ciam gam sungah note’ suanlekhakte le na gam sung panun a piangte, na an uh le na leenggahzu uh le na sathau uh, le na ganhingte uh pungsakin, na tuulekeelno honte uh zong thupha pia ding hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Midangte khempeuh sangin note thupha hong kilim piakzaw ding hi. Note’ lak hitaleh na ganhingte uh lak hitaleh ah a nu ahi a, a pa ahi zongin a ciing om lo ding hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Topa in note’ tung panin natna khempeuh lakhia ding hi. Note in na theihsa uh ahi Egypt gam a natna siate note’ tungah khat zong hong tung lo ding a, ahih hangin no hong mudahte khempeuh tungah tuate tungsak ding hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Topa na Pasian un note tungah hong piak mi khempeuh na beisak ding uh a, amaute na khasiat kei ding uh hi. Note a dingin thangzak hi ding ahih manin amau’ pasian-te zong na bia kei ding uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Na lungsim uhah, ‘Hih minamte ei sangin tamzaw hi. Amaute bangci suankhiat zawh ding ihi hiam?’ na cih khak uhleh,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> amaute na kihta kei ding uh hi. Topa na Pasian un Faro le Egypt mite khempeuh tungah a hih,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na mitte un a muhsa a lian ze-etnate, limte, na lamdangte, a vangliatna le Topa na Pasian un hong paikhiatpihna a thahatna na phawk ding uh hi. Topa na Pasian un na kihtak uh mi khempeuh tungah tua bangin hih ding hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tua tham loin, a omlai mite le no kiang panin a bu mite a siat khit dong matengin Topa na Pasian un amaute’ lakah tunpi khah ding hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Note in amaute na kihta kei ding uh hi; bang hang hiam cih leh a lian a kihtakhuai ahi Pasian, Topa na Pasian uh note tawh a om hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Topa na Pasian un note’ mai-ah hih minamte tawm tawmin siang khiasak ding hi. Note a dingin gamsate hong tam khanlua kha ding ahih manin thakhatthu-in amaute na beisak kei ding uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ahih hangin Topa na Pasian un note tungah amaute hong pia ding a, amaute a bei matengin kibuaisak ding hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Amah in note’ khut sungah amaute’ kumpite hong pia ding a, note in mun khempeuh panin amaute’ min na maimangsak ding uh hi. Amaute na susiamang khin ding uh a, note’ langkhatah mi khat beek hong pang zo lo ding hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> A kiseek amau’ pasian milimte mei tawh na hal ding uh hi. Tua nate-ah na awk khak loh nadingun amaute’ tunga a om kham le ngun deihgawh loin, note a dingin na la kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh tua pen Topa na Pasian uh tungah a kihhuai ahi hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Note’ inn sungah a kihhuai nate na tumpih kei ding uh a, tua nate tawh kibangin samsiat a thuak mi na kisuaksak kei ding uh hi. Note in tua nate mudah mahmahin na kih ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh tua nate a kisamsia na ahi hi."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Note nungta-in tampi na phak theih nading uh le na pu na pate uh tungah piak dinga Topa a kiciamsa leitangah va pai-in na neih theih nadingun tuni-a note kiangah kong gen thupiakna khempeuh limtakin na zuih ding uh na ngaihsun ding uh hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A thupiakte na zui uh hiam, na zui kei uh hiam cih a theih nadingin note hong niamkhiatin, na lungsim uhah bang om hiam cih a theih nadingin Topa na Pasian un sehnel gamah hih kum sawmli sung note hong paipihna lampi khempeuh na ciamteh ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Mite, an bek tawh nungta loin Topa’ kamsung panin a pusuak thu khempeuh tawh nungta hi, ci-in note hong theihsak nadingin, amah in note hong niamkhiatin hong gilkialsak a, note hitaleh na pu na pate uh hitaleh in a theih ngei loh manna tawh hong vak hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hih kum sawmli sung note’ tunga om na puan uh sia loin, na khe uh zong bawk lo hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tua ahih manin mi khat in a tapa a khal bangin Topa na Pasian un note hong khalna thu na lungsim uhah thei un.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tua ahih ciangin ama lampi zuihna le amah zahtakna tawh Topa note Pasian’ thupiakte na zui ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa note’ Pasian in, mual le guamah a luang tuite a omna, ciktui le tuikhuk a omna leitang,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> mangbuh le mangbuhham, leenggui le theikung, le mang kawlsing a omna leitang, oliv kungte le khuaizu a omna leitang,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bangmah kisam loin, cilbawl loin an na nek nading uh leitang, a suangte sik ahihna leitang, mualte sung panin sumsan na tawh theihna uh leitang ahi gam hoihah note hong paipih hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Note in ne-in na gil uh vah ding a, note tungah gam hoih hong piakna hangin Topa na Pasian uh na phat ding uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Tuni-a no tungah kong gen ahi ama thupiaknate le a ngeina kipte le a thukhamte zuih lohna tawh Topa na Pasian uh mangngilh kha ding na hih manun kidawm un.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tua hikeileh, an ne-in na kham uh ciang, inn hoihte lamin tuate sungah na ten uh ciang,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na bawnghonte uh le na tuuhonte uh tampi a phak ciang le na khamte uh le na ngunte uh tampi pha-in, na neih khempeuh uh tampi a phak ciangin",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na lungsim uh lianin, salsuahna Egypt gam panin note a hong paikhiatpih,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> a lian a lauhuai sehnel gamah gul gunei le momai lak le tui om lohna lei keu-ah a hong paipihpa, meisuang tawh a kibang suangpi panin tui a hong piapa,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> a tawpna-ah a hoihin na gamtat theih nading uh a deihna-in note hong niamkhiatin a hong ze-et theih nadingin na pu na pate un a theih loh manna tawh sehnel gamah a hong vak Topa na Pasian uh na mangngilh kha ding uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na lungsim uhah, ‘Ka vangliatna uh le ka thahatna un hih hauhna hong ngahsak hi,’ ci kha ding na hih manun kingaihsun un.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tuni-a mah bangin na pu na pate uh tungah a kiciamna a kipsak theih nadingin, na hauh nadingun vangliatna a hong piapa amah ahih manin Topa na Pasian uh na phawk ding uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Topa na Pasian uh mangngilhin pasian dangte’ nung zui-in tuate’ na semin na biak uhleh, na sia taktak ding uh hi, ci-in tuni-in limtakin kong hilhkhol hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Topa note’ Pasian’ aw ngai lo ahih manun, Topa in note’ mai-ah a siatsak minamte bangin note na sia ding uh hi."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Israel-te aw, za un; note sangin tamzaw-in a thahatzaw minamte, lianin van banin kulhpi a kiciangto khuapite, na theihsa uh mi ahi a pum lian a tun sang Anak mite, ‘Anak mite, kua in dozo ding ahi hiam?’ a kicih na zak ngei mite uh a suankhia dingin Jordan a kantan ta ding na hi uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tua ahih ciangin, a kangtum thei mei bangin note’ mai-ah a pai pa pen Topa na Pasian uh ahihna thu tuni-in thei un. Amah in note’ mai-ah amaute susia-in, amaute zogawp ding hi. Tua ahih ciangin Topa in note tungah hong ciamsa bangin amaute hawlkhia-in manlangin na siamangsak ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Topa na Pasian un note mai panin amaute a nawhkhiat khit ciangin, na lungsim uhah, ‘Hih leitang a luah dingin Topa in hong paipihna pen komau’ thumanna hang ahi hi,’ ci kha kei un. Topa in na mai uhah amaute a hawlkhiatna pen hih minamte’ gitlohna hang hizaw hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na thumanna hang uh ahi a, na lungsim manna hang uh tawh ahi zongin amau’ leitang a luah ding na hi kei uh hi. Topa na Pasian un na mai panun amaute a hawlkhiatna pen hih minamte’ gitlohna hang le Topa in na pu na pate uh Abraham, Isaac, le Jakob tungah a thuciamna kammal a kipsak theih nading ahi hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin note’ thumanna hangin Topa na Pasian un na tan’ dingun hih leitang hoih note tungah hong pia ahihlohna thei un. Bang hang hiam cih leh note pen lungsim khauh mi na hi uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Topa na Pasian uh sehnel gamah phinin na hehsakna uh phawk unla, mangngilh kei un. Egypt gam panin na paikhiat ni uh a kipan hih lai na tun dongun Topa langpanin na lehdo uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Horeb mual nangawnah a heh nadingin Topa na phin uh a, note’ tungah Topa heh a, amah in note hong susia dektak hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Topa in note tawh a bawl thuciamna suangpeekte a sang dingin mualtungah ka paitoh lai-in, mualtungah sun sawmli le zan sawmli sung ka om a, an ne lo, tui dawn loin ka om hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Pasian’ khut tawh a kigelh suangpek nihte kei tungah Topa in hong pia hi. Kikhop ni-in mei sung panin note tungah Topa in hong gensa kammal khempeuh tua suangpeekte tungah om hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Sun sawmli le zan sawmli a cin ni-in kiciamna suangpek nihte Topa in kei hong pia hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Tua ciangin Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Kithawi inla, hih lai panin paisuk mengmeng in. Bang hang hiam cih leh Egypt panin na paikhiatpih mite a sia-in gamta khin uh hi. Amaute ka thupiakna panin kiheikhia pak uh a, amaute a dingin a kisung milim khat bawl khin uh hi,’ hong ci hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Tua tham loin Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Hih mite ka mu khin a, a lungsim khauh mite ahi hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Amaute susia-in mun khempeuh panin amaute’ min ka phiat theihna dingin kei guak hong omsak in. Amaute sangin a vanglianzaw, a tamzaw minamin nang kong bawl ding hi,’ hong ci lai hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin kihei-in mualtung panin kong paisuk a, mei in mual kangin na kuang hi. Kiciamna suangpek nihte ka khut nihte sungah om hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tua ciangin ka khuadak leh, Topa na Pasian tung uhah na khial khin takpi uh a, a kisung bawngno milim amaute a dingin na bawl uh hi. Topa in note hong thupiakna panin na kiheikhia pak uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tua ahih ciangin suangpek nihte la-in ka khut nihte’ sung panin lawnin note’ muhna-ah ka sukham hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tua ciangin a masa-a bangin sun sawmli le zan sawmli sung Topa’ mai-ah kunin ka om a, ama heh nadingin phinin, Topa’ muhna-ah a sia gamtatna tawh note’ khialhnate khempeuh hangin an ne lo, tui dawn loin ka om hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh note’ tungah Topa’ hehna le a lungkim hetlohna, note susia dingin a kithawina hangin ka lau hi. Ahih hangin tua hunin zong Topa in kei’ thu hong ngai hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Aaron’ tungah Topa heh mahmah a, amah susia dingin kithawi a, tua hun mahin Aaron a’ ding zong thu ka ngen hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tua ciangin note’ khialhna, na bawlsa uh bawngno, mei tawh halin sukhamin, leivui bangin a neel dongin ka gawizan hi. Tua ciangin mualtung panin a hong luangsuk lui sungah a vuite ka lawn hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Taberah, Massah, le Kibrothhattaavah munte-ah zong Topa phinin na hehsak uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Topa in Kadeshbarnea panin note hong sawlin, ‘Paito unla note kong piak leitang luah un,’ hong cih lai-in Topa na Pasian uh hong thupiakna nialin, amah um loin, ama aw na ngai kei uh hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Note kong theih ni a kipan Topa na nial uh hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin Topa in note ka susia ding ci ahih manin hih sun sawmli le zan sawmli sung Topa’ mai-ah kunin ka om hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Topa’ tungah thu ka ngen a, ‘Topa Pasian aw, nangmah in na liatna tawh na hotkhiatsa, na vangliatna tawh Egypt panin na paikhiatpih na mite le na luahte susia kei in.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na nasem Abraham, Isaac, le Jakob phawk inla, hih mihingte’ lungsim khauhna hitaleh a gitlohna uh hitaleh a khialhna uh hitaleh thusim kei in.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Tua bang hikeileh kote nong paikhiatpihna gam mite in, “Topa in amaute tungah a ciamsa leitangah amaute paipih zo loin, amah in amaute mudah ahih manin, sehnel gamah amaute a that dingin paikhiatpih hi,” ci kha ding uh hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute pen na vangliatna le na thahatna tawh na paikhiatpih na mihingte le na luahte ahi hi,’ ka ci hi."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Tua hun laitakin Topa in kei kiangah, ‘A masa-a bangin suangpek nih seekin, mualtung ka kiangah hong pai inla, sing singkuang khat bawl in.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A masa-a suangpek na sukkhapte’ tunga thute tua suangpeekte tungah ka gelh ding a, singkuang sungah tuate na koih ding hi,’ hong ci hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin singkha sing tawh singkuang khat bawlin, a masa-a bangin suangpek nih ka seek a, ka khut sungah a peek nihte tawi-in mualtungah ka paito hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kikhop ni-in mei sung panin mualtungah Topa in note tungah hong gensa thupiak sawmte, a masa-a a kigelh bangin tua suangpeekte tungah amah in gelh a, tua ciangin Topa in kei tungah tua suangpeekte hong pia hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tua ciangin kihei-in mualtung panin ka paisuk a, ka bawlsa singkuang sungah tua suangpeekte ka koih hi. Topa in kei hong thupiak bangin suangpeekte tua sungah a om hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> (Beeroth Benejaakan panin Moserah-ah Israel mite zin uh hi. Tua lai-ah Aaron si a, tua lai munah kivui hi. Ama tangin a tapa Eleazar in siampi na sem hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tua lai panin Gudgodah-ah pai uh a, Gudgodah panin lui tuite a omna gam Jotbathah-ah pai uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tua hun laitakin Topa in, tuni dongin ama na a sem ding le ama min tawh thupha a pia dingin Topa’ mai-ah dingin, Topa’ thuciamna singkuang a pua dingin Levi minamte a tuam koih hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tua ahih ciangin a sanggamte uh bangin Levi mite in tanh ahi a, luah ahi zongin nei lo uh a, Topa na Pasian un amau kiangah a gen bangin Topa pen amau’ luah ahi hi.)",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “A masa-a bangin sun sawmli le zan sawmli sung mualtungah ka om a, Topa in tua hunin zong ka thu hong ngai a, Topa in note hong susia nawn lo hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Amaute tungah piak dingin a pu a pate uh tungah ka kiciam leitangah pai-in a luah theih nadingun ding inla, na khualzin uh zomin mite mai-ah pai in,’ hong ci hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Israel-te aw, tu-in, Topa na Pasian uh zahtak ding, ama lampite tot ding, amah it ding, na lungsim khempeuh uh le na nuntakna khempeuh uh tawh Topa note’ Pasian’ na sep ding,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> le nomau’ hoih nadingin tuni-a kong gen thupiaknate le Topa’ thukhamte zuih ding cih simloh, Topa na Pasian un note’ tung panin bang dang hong kal ahi hiam?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> En un, vantung le vantung a sangpente le leitung le a sunga om khempeuh pen Topa note’ Pasian-a’ ahi hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tua hi napi-in Topa in na pu na pate uh a itna lian mahmah ahih manin tuni-a mah bangin midangte khempeuh sangin amau’ suanlekhakte hong teelzaw hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tua ahih ciangin Topa’ thu mang unla, lungkhauh nawn kei un.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian uh a lian, a vanglian, a kihtakhuai Pasian, angvan nei loin, sumgolh a la lo, pasian-te’ Pasian, topate’ Topa ahi hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Amah in pa nei lote le meigong numeite a dingin thutang semin, peemtate itin an le puan a pia hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tua ahih ciangin peemtate it un; bang hang hiam cih leh note zong Egypt gamah peemta na hi uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Topa note’ Pasian na zahtak ding uh a, ama na semin, amah beelin, ama min tawh na kiciam ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Amah pen nomau’ phat ding ahi hi. Na mitte un a muhsa hih a lian a kihtakhuai nate note a dingin hong bawlsak pa pen na Pasian uh ahi hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na pu na pate uh mihing sawmsagih bek Egypt-ah paisuk uh a, ahi zongin tu-in Topa na Pasian un vantung aksi zahin note hong tamsak hi."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin Topa na Pasian uh itin ama hong thuhilhna, a thukhamte, a ngeina kipte, a thupiakte na zui tawntung ding uh hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tuni-in ngaihsun un (a thei nai lo, a mu nai lo na tate uh tungah a gen hi lo ka hih ciangin), Topa note’ Pasian’ hong thuhilhna, ama liatna, a vangliatna le a thahatna,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Egypt kumpipa Faro le a leitang tung khempeuhah a hih Egypt gam sunga ama limte le a sepnate;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Egypt galkapte, a sakolte le a leengte tungah a hihte; note hong delh laitakin San Tuipi tawh amaute tuumsakin, tuni dongin Topa in amaute a suksiatna;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> hih mun na tun ma sungtengun sehnel gamah amah in note tungah hong hihte;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Reuben’ tapa Eliab, a tapa Dathan le Abiram-te tungah a hihte; leitang a kam ka-in Israel khempeuh lakah a innkuanpihte, a puanbukte le amau a zuite khempeuh tawh amaute a nawmvalhna ngaihsun un.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa’ hihsa a nasepna a liante khempeuh na mitte un mu khin hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin note thahatin, na luah ding uh leitangah va pai-in na luah theih nading uh le, Topa in na pu na pate uh le a suanlekhakte uh tungah piak dingin a kiciam, bawngnawi le khuaizu tui bangin a luanna gamah sauvei na nuntak theih nadingun tuni-a kong gen thupiakna khempeuh na zui ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh luah dinga na lut nading uh leitang pen note’ hong paikhiatna, anteh cinna huan banga khaici vawhin tui na buah nadingun nakpitakin na semin tui na lakna uh Egypt leitang tawh kibang lo hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Note va pai-in na luah ding uh leitang pen, vantung panin guahtui a ngah mual le guam a omna leitang,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Topa na Pasian un a kep leitang hi a, kum kipat a kipan kum bei dongin Topa note’ Pasian in tua leitang en tawntung hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Topa na Pasian uh itin, na lungsim khempeuh uh le na nuntakna khempeuh uh tawh ama na na sep nadingun tuni-a kong gen ama thupiaknate na zuih uhleh,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na an uh le na leenggahzu uh le na sathau uh na kaihkhop theih nadingun amah in guah masa le guah nunung, a hunin na leitang uh a dingin hong zusak ding hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Amah in na ganhingte uh a dingin na gam sung uhah lopa hong posak ding a, note in zong an ne-in na gil uh vah ding hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Midangte’ hong khemna hangin note kihei-in pasian dangte’ na semin tuate na biakkhak loh nadingun kingaihsun un.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tua hikeileh no tungah Topa hong hehin guah zu lo ding a, leitang in bangmah piangsak loin, Topa in no hong piak leitang hoihah manlangin na siat pak theihna dingun amah in vantungte khakcip kha ding hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin hih ka thugente na lungsim uhah ciamtehin na ngaihsun ding uh hi. Na khut tung uhah lim dingin na khih ding uh a, tuate pen na mitte uh kikalah talsuan hi ding hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na tate uh tungah na hilh ding uh a, na innsung uhah na lut laitak, lampi-ah na pai laitak, na lup ciang uhleh na thawh ciangun tuate genin na nei ding uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Vantungte, leitung’ tungah a om laiteng, amaute tungah piak dingin Topa in na pu na pate uh tungah a kiciam gam sungah note le na tate uh khan a sau theih nadingin na inn kongkhak khuam uh le na kongpite uh tungah tuate na gelh ding uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian uh itin, ama lampi khempeuh zui-in, amah beelin, nomau zuih dingin kong gen hih thupiakna khempeuh zuih ding na kingaihsut uhleh,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Topa in na mai uhah a om hih minamte khempeuh hawlkhia ding a, note sangin lianzaw-in a thahatzaw minamte na suankhia ding uh hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na khe un a sikna mun khempeuh nomau a’ hi ding hi. Na gamgi uh sehnel gam panin Lebanon ciang dong le Eufratis gun panin nitumna tuipi dong hi ding hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na lang uhah kuamah pang zo lo ding hi. No tungah hong ciam bangin Topa na Pasian un na tot ding uh gam khempeuh tungah note hong kizahtakna le note hong kikihtakna tungsak ding hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “En un, tuni-in na mai uhah thupha khat le hamsia khat ka koih hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Tuni-a kong gen, Topa na Pasian uh thupiaknate na zuih uhleh thupha hi a,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Topa na Pasian uh thupiaknate mang loin, na theih nai loh uh pasian dangte’ nungzui dingin tuni-a no kong thupiakna panin na kiheikhiat uh le hamsia ahi hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Luah dingin na lutna uh leitangah Topa na Pasian un hong paipih ciangin Gerizim Mual tungah thupha taangko-in, Ebal Mual tungah hamsia na taangko ding uh hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> (Tua mualte, Jordan gal, lampi panin nitumna lam, Moreh tawsaw gei-a Gilgal galkhat, Arabah-ah a teng Kanaan mite’ gam sungah om hi.)",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian un note hong piak leitang a luah dingin Jordan kantanin a pai ding na hi uh hi. Tua leitang luahin a sungah na ten uh ciangin,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> tuni-a note kong piak thukhamte le ngeina kipte khempeuh na zuih ding uh limtakin na ngaihsun ding uh hi."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Hihte pen, leitungah na nuntak laiteng uh Topa, na pu na pate uh Pasian in na neih dingun no hong piaksa gam sungah limtakin na zuih ding uh thukhamte le ngeina kipte ahi hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na suankhiat ding uh minamte in a biakna mun mual sangte tung le mual neute tung le singniim nuai, mun khempeuh na susia taktak ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Amaute’ biakna taute phelkhia-in, a biakna songte dengzanin, amaute’ Asherah milimte mei tawh na hal ding uh hi. A kiseek amau’ pasian-te’ limte na phukpai ding uh a, tua mun panin amau’ min na maimangsak ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Ahih hangin Topa na Pasian uh tungah tua bangin na hih kei ding uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Topa na Pasian un na minam khempeuh uh sung panin ama min koih nadingin teelin, ama omna dinga a bawlna mun na zong ding uh hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tua lai-ah na pai ding uh a, na meihal biaknate uh le na biakpiaknate uh, note in na piak uh sawm-ah-khat le na piak thuahte uh, thuciamna biakpiakna, utthu-a na piakna, na bawnghon tacilte uh le na tuuhon tacilte uh tua lai-ah na paipih ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Topa na Pasian uh mai tua lai munah na ne ding uh a, Topa na Pasian un note thupha hong piakna hangin na hihna khempeuh uhah note le na innkuanpihte na lungdam ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Tua hun ciangin mi khempeuh in ama hoihsak bangin a gamtat ngei ciat bangin na gamta nawn kei ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian un note hong piak tawlngakna le luahna-ah na tung nai kei uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ahih hangin Jordan galkhatah pai-in, Topa na Pasian un luah dingin note hong piak leitangah tengin, nuamtakin na nuntak theih nadingun na kiim uha na langte khempeuh uh kiang panin tawlngakna hong piak ciangin,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Topa na Pasian un ama min om nading munin a teelna munah note kong sawl khempeuh na paipih ding uh hi. Na meihal biaknate uh le na biakpiaknate uh, note in na piak uh sawm-ah-khat le na piak thuahte uh le Topa’ tungah na ciam uh na thuciam piaknate uh na paipih ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah note le na tapate uh le na tanute uh, na nasem numeite uh le na nasem pasalte uh, le note’ neih bangin tanh ahi a, luah ahi zongin a nei lo na khuasung uha om Levi mite tawh lungdam khawm un.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na tuahna mun peuh uhah na meihal biaknate uh na piak loh nadingun kingaihsun un.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na minamte uh sung panin Topa in a teelna mun khatah na meihal biaknate uh pia-in, note kong thupiakte khempeuh tua lai munah na hih ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Ahi zongin, Topa na Pasian un note tungah hong piak thupha tawh kizui-in na khuapite uh khat peuhpeuh sungah sa na deih zahzah uh go-in na ne thei ding uh hi. Sanang le sakhitalte a kinek mah bangin mi a nin le a siang kideidan loin na ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> A si na ne kei bek ding uh hi; tui bangin leitungah a si na bua ding uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na an uh sawm-ah-khat ahi a, na leenggahzu uh ahi a, na sathau uh ahi zongin, na bawnghon uh le na tuuhonte uh sung pan tacilte ahi zongin, na kiciamna uh ahi na thuciam uh biakpiakna khat peuhpeuh ahi zongin, utthu-a na piakte uh ahi zongin, nomau’ piak thuahte ahi zongin na khuapite uh sungah na ne thei kei ding uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Topa na Pasian un a teelna munah note le na tapate le na tanute, na nasem numeite le na nasem pasalte, le na khuapite uh sunga om Levi mite in Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah na ne ding uh hi. Na hihna khempeuh uhah Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah na lungdam ding uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na gam sung uhah na ten laiteng uh Levi mite na mangngilh loh nadingun kingaihsun un.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “No tungah hong ciamsa bangin Topa na Pasian un na gamgi uh hong sotsak ciangin, sa na duh manun, ‘Sa ka ne ding uh hi,’ na cih uhleh, na duh zahzah uh sa na ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Topa na Pasian un ama min koih nadingin a teelna mun pen note kiang panin a gamla lua ahihleh, note kong thupiaksa bangin Topa in no hong piaksa na bawnghon uh pan ahi a, na tuuhon uh pan ahi zongin khat peuhpeuh na go thei ding uh a, na duh zahzah uh na khuasung uhah na ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sanang ahi a, sakhital ahi zongin a kinek mah bangin na ne thei ding uh a, mi a nin le a siang kideidan loin a kibangin na ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> A si na nek loh ding uh theitel un. Bang hang hiam cih leh si pen nuntakna hi a, nuntakna pen sa tawh na ne khawm kei ding uh hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Si na ne kei ding uh a, tui bangin leitungah na buakhia ding uh hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Topa’ muhna-ah a manin na gamtat uh ciangin note le note’ khit cianga na tate uh a nopsak theih nadingin si na ne kei ding uh hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ahih hangin na bat uh a siangtho nate le na thuciamna uh na piaknate uh note in la-in Topa in a teelna munah na paipih ding uh a,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Topa na Pasian uh biakna tau tungah na meihal biakna uh, a sa le a si na pia ding uh hi. Na biakpiakna uh site Topa note’ Pasian’ biakna tau tungah kibuakhia ding a, ahih hangin a sa na ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Topa na Pasian uh muhna-ah a hoih le a manin na gamtat uh ciangin note le note’ khit cianga na tate uh a nopsak theih nadingin note kong thupiak khempeuh na kin ding uh limtakin ngaihsun un.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Topa na Pasian un na mai panun na suankhiat ding uh minamte beimangsakin, amaute suankhia-in amau’ leitangah na ten uh ciangin,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> na mai uhah amaute a kisuksiat khit ciangin amaute zui-in na awk khak loh nading uh le, ‘Kei zong amau’ hih bangin ka hih theih nadingin hih minamte in a pasian-te uh bangci biak ahi uh hiam?’ ci-in a pasian-te uh thu na kan loh nadingun kingaihsun un.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Topa na Pasian uh tungah tua bangin na hih kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa in a muhdah a kihhuai nam khempeuh amaute in a pasian-te uh a dingin hih uh hi. A pasian-te uh a dingin a tapate uh le a tanute nangawn uh mei sungah a hal uh hi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Note kong thupiak khempeuh na hih ding uh na lim ngaihsut ding uh hi. Na behlap kei ding uh a, zong na khiam kei ding uh hi."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Note lakah kamsang khat ahi a, mangman khat ahi zongin hong khangin, lim ahi a, nalamdang ahi zongin hong lak a,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ama hong gen lim ahi a, nalamdang ahi zongin hong tungin, na theih ngei loh uh, ‘Adang pasian-te’ nung zui-in amaute va bia ni,’ hong cih leh,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> tua kamsangpa’ thu ahi a, mangman pa’ thu ahi zongin na ngai kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa note’ Pasian na lungsim khempeuh uh le na nuntakna khempeuh uh tawh na it uh hiam cih a kitheih nadingin Topa na Pasian un no hong ze-etna ahi hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Topa na Pasian uh nung zui-in, amah na zahtak ding uh a, a thupiaknate zui-in a thu na ngai ding uh a, amah bia-in amah na beel ding uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ahih hangin tua kamsangpa ahi a, mangman pa ahi zongin kithat ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian un na pai nadingun a hong thupiak na nusiat theih nading uh le Egypt leitang panin hong paikhiatpihin salsuahna panin hong honkhia Topa na Pasian uh langpangin na lehdo nading uh thu hong hilh ahi hi. Tua bangin note’ lak panin siatna na siangkhiasak ding uh hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Na sanggampa ahi a, na tanu ahih kei leh na tapa in ahi a, na ang sunga om na zi ahi a, nangmah banga na ngaihsut na lawm it in ahi zongin nang hong zol simin, leimong khat pan mong khat dong kikalah, nang kiang pan a nai ahi a, a gamla ahi zongin, nang hitaleh na pu na pate hitaleh in a theih ngei loh, na kiima om mite’ pasian-te, ‘Va pai-in pasian dangte va bia ni,’ hong cih leh",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ama cih mang loin, a thu ngai loin, amah hehpih loin, amah khahkhong loin, amah na im kei ding hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nangmah in amah na that ding hi. Amah a that dingin nangmah a masa pen na hi ding a, tua khit ciangin midangte khempeuh in hong zui ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Salsuahna ahi Egypt gam panin a hong paikhiatpih Topa na Pasian uh kiang panin note hong paikhiatpih ding ngaihsun ahih manin suang tawh amah na denglum ding uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tua ciangin Israel-te khempeuh in za-in lau ding uh a, hih banga gitlohna note lakah bawlkik ngei nawn lo ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Topa na Pasian un tenna dinga hong piak na khuapite uh khat peuhpeuh sungah,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> mi ginalo pawlkhat note lakah hong pai-in, ‘Pai-in pasian dangte va bia ni,’ ci-in na theih ngei lohte uh lamah khuapi sunga teng mite a paikhiatpihna na zak uhleh,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> note in a thu na kan ding uh a, zongin limtakin na dong ding uh hi. Note lakah tua banga a kihhuai-in gamtatna thu a om mah ahih takpi leh,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> tua khua sunga mite namsau tawh na that ding uh a, khua sunga om mi khempeuh le a ganhingte, namsau tawh na susiamang ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Note in van kinusiate khempeuh khua laizang mun awngah khawmin, Topa na Pasian uh tungah khuapi le van kinusia khempeuh meihal biakna bupin mei tawh na hal ding uh hi. Tua khuapi pen ninkikholna hi tawntung ding a, kilamkik nawn lo ding hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tuni-a kong gen ama thupiaknate khempeuh zui-in Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah a manin gamtatna tawh Topa na Pasian uh’ aw na ngaih uhleh, na pu na pate uh tungah a ciamsa bangin, a kihtakhuai ama hehna panin Topa kihei-in note tungah migitna hong lakin, note tungah hehpihna hong nei-in, note tampi tak hong phaksak theih nadingin a ki-apsa na khat beek zong note a dingin na kem kei ding uh hi."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Note pen Topa na Pasian uh mite na hi uh hi. Misite hangin note ki-atkeh loin, na sam uh zong na mettol kei ding uh hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh note pen Topa na Pasian uh tungah a siangtho mite na hi uh a, leitung a om mite khempeuh sung panin ama neih dingin Topa in note hong teel ahi hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “A kihhuai na khat peuhpeuh na ne kei ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na nek theih ding uh ganhingte: Bawng, tuu, keel,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> sakhital, sanang, simsakhi, sathak, saza, zosakhi, le gamtuu ahi hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ganhingte lak panin a khecin a ka, eknel a hai ganhing peuhmah na ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ahi zongin eknel a hai a, a khecin a ka ahi zongin na nek theih loh dingte uh: Kalaoh, bilpi, le sakikhte in eknel a hai hangin a khecin ka lo ahih manin note a dingin a nin ahi hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Vok pen a khecin a kat hangin eknel hai lo ahih manin note-a’ dingin a nin ahi hi. Tuate’ sa ne loin, a sisate zong na lawng kei ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Tui sunga om khempeuh lak panin phe le lip a nei peuhmah na ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Phe le lip a nei lo peuhmah na ne kei ding uh a, tuate pen no-a’ dingin a nin ahi hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Vasa a siang khempeuh na ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ahih hangin na nek loh dingte uh: Muvanlai, musane, luimu,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> mupi, mumeika, amau nam ciat;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> va-ak nam khempeuh;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> vasa-kalaoh, pengpelep, vatawt, musi nam khempeuh;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> keising le simbu, gam vatawt",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> le tui vatawt, samuat ne musane le tuimu,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> gun vapi, gun vazonei nam khempeuh; huihtun le bak ahi hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Kha a nei insek ganhing khempeuh no a dingin a nin ahi hi; tuate kine lo ding hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> A leng thei insek ganhing a siangte khempeuh na ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Ama thu-a a si tawm ganhing peuhmah na ne kei ding uh hi. A nek dingun na khuasung uha om khualmite tungah na pia thei ding uh a, tua ahih kei leh zong gamdang mite tungah na zuak thei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh note pen Topa na Pasian uh tungah a siangtho mi na hi uh hi. “Keelno a pi’ nawizu tawh na huan kei ding uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “A kum kumin na lo uhah a piang, na khaici panun a piang khempeuh sawm-ah-khat na pia ding uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Topa na Pasian uh na zahtak tawntung nading uh na theih nadingun, ama min a ten nadingin a teelna mun Topa note’ Pasian’ mai-ah na an uh, na leenggahzu uh, na sathau uh sawm-ah-khat, le na bawnghon uh le na tuuhon tacilte uh na ne ding uh hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Topa na Pasian un a min koih nadingin a teelna mun pen, Topa na Pasian un no thupha hong piak ciangin note kiang panin gamla lua a, no a dingin lam a sau luat manin sawm-ah-khat na paipih zawh kei uhleh,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> tuate sum na suah ding uh a, a sumte tunin, Topa na Pasian un a teelna munah na pai ding uh a,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na deih peuhpeuh uh bawng ahi a, tuu ahi a, leenggahzu ahi a, khamtheihzu ahi zongin, na duh peuhpeuh uh leina-in a sum na zang ding uh hi. Topa na Pasian uh mai tua lai munah na ne ding uh a, note le na innkuanpihte uh na lungdam ding uh hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Note bangin amaute in tanh le luah nei lo ahih manin na khuasung uha om Levi mite na mangngilh kei ding uh hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Kum thum simin tua kum-a note’ anpiang sawm-ah-khat khempeuh hong paikhiatpihin na khuasung uhah na khol ding uh hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Topa na Pasian un na sepnate khempeuh uhah thupha hong piak theih nadingin, note tawh kibangin amaute in tanh ahi a, luah ahi zongin nei lo uh ahih manin note’ khua sunga om Levi mite, peemtate, pa nei lote, leh meigong numeite hong pai-in tua ante ne-in a gilvah ding uh hi."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Kum sagih a cin simin leiba maisakna na nei ding uh hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Maisak nading zia in: Leitawi a pia mi khempeuh in a vengte tungah leitawi a a piaksate maisak ding hi. Topa’ maisakna thu kigen khin ahih manin a vengpa, a sanggampa’ tung pan kuamah in leiba siik nawn lo ding hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Gamdang mite’ tung pan na siik thei ding uh a, ahih hangin na sanggamte uh tung panin no-a’ hong bat peuhmah na maisak ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Ahih hangin tuni-a kong gen hih thupiakna khempeuh zui-in Topa note’ Pasian’ aw na ngaih nak-uhleh note’ lakah a zawng om lo ding hi (bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian un na neih dingun gamhluahin hong piak leitang tungah Topa in note thupha hong pia ding hi).",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian un hong ciamsa bangin note thupha hong pia ding a, minam tampi tungah leitawi na pia ding uh a, ahih hangin note in lei na tawi kei ding uh hi. Minam tampite na uk ding uh a, ahih hangin amaute in note hong uk lo ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Topa na Pasian un note hong piak gam sunga na khuate uh khat peuhpeuh sungah na sanggam khat uh note lakah a zawng a om leh na lungsim uh khauhsak loin, na sanggam zawng pa uh huh loin na om kei ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ama tungah na cingh gamtat ding uh a, bangbang hitaleh ama kisap zah na leitawi ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na lungsim uhah ngaihsutna hoih lo omin, ‘Kum sagihna, maisakna kum hong nai hi,’ ci-in na sanggampa galmi et-in amah bangmah na piak loh uh ciangin na langkhatah Topa’ tungah amah kiko-in, no tungah khialhna a suahkhak ding kingaihsun un.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Citna tawh amah na pia ding uh a, amah na piak uh ciangin lungsim neihna na nei kei ding uh hi. Topa na Pasian un na sepna na hihna khempeuh uhah hih thu hangin note thupha hong pia ding hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh leitang tungah mizawng bei ngei lo ding hi. Tua ahih ciangin, ‘Gam sungah a om na sanggampa, na a kisam mite le mizawngte tungah na cingh mahmah ding uh hi,’ ci-in thu kong pia hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Na sanggampa, Hebru pasal khat ahi a, Hebru numei khat ahi zongin nang tungah hong kizuak leh, amah in nangma na kum guk sung hong sem ding a, a kum sagihna ciangin nang kiang panin a suakta-in na paikhiasak ding hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na kiang panin a suakta-in na paikhiatsak ciangin khuthawm guakin na paisak kei ding hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na tuuhon lak, na ancilna le na leenggah sukna panin citna tawh tampi na pia ding a, Topa na Pasian in nang thupha hong piak zahin amah na pia ding hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Egypt gamah sila na hihna uh le Topa na Pasian un note hong suahtaksakna na phawk ding uh hi. Tua ahih manin hih thu tuni-in kong pia hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ahih hangin amah in note nuam hong sa-in, nang le na innkuanpihte hong it ahih manin ‘Nang kiang panin ka paikhia kei ding hi,’ hong cih leh,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> phimpi khat la-in, kongkhak dapphahin a bil na vut ding a, na sila hi tawntung ding hi. Na sila numei zong tua bangmahin na hih ding hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na kiang panin a suakta-in amah na paisak ciangin haksa sa kei in; bang hang hiam cih leh a kicial nasem thaman lang tawh amah in nangma na kum guk sung hong sem khinzo hi. Tua ahih ciangin Topa na Pasian un na hihna khempeuh uhah thupha hong pia ding hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Na bawnghon uh le na tuuhon uh panin tacil a pa khempeuh Topa note’ Pasian’ tungah na ap ding uh hi. Na bawnghon tacilte uh tawh na na sem kei ding uh a, na tuuhon tacilte uh zong a mul na met kei ding uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Topa in a teelna munah a kum kumin Topa note’ Pasian’ mai-ah na innkuanpihte uh tawh na ne ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ahih hangin poina khatpeuh, a khebai a mittaw, ahih kei leh poina lian khat peuhpeuh a neih leh, Topa note’ Pasian’ tungah biakna-in na pia kei ding uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na khuasung uhah na ne ding uh hi. Sanang ahi a, sakhi ahi zongin a kinek bangin mi nin le mi siangte in a kibangin ne thei ding uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> A si na ne kei bek ding uh a, tui bangin leilakah a si na buakhia ding uh hi."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Abib kha tang unla, Topa na Pasian uh a dingin Paisan Pawi bawl un. Bang hang hiam cih leh Abib kha sungin Topa na Pasian un Egypt gam panin zanin note hong paikhiatpih hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Tuuhon pan ahi a, bawnghon pan ahi zongin Topa in ama min om nadingin a teelna munah Paisan Pawi biakpiakna Topa na Pasian uh tungah na pia ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Silngo sawh anlum tawh na ne kei ding uh a, ni sagih sung silngo sawh loh anlum, gimna anlum tawh na ne ding uh hi. Egypt gam panin nawhsa-in na taikhia uh hi. Egypt gam panin na taikhiat uh hun na nuntak sung tawntung uh na phawk theih nading uh ahi hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na gam sung khempeuh uhah ni sagih sung note lakah silngo kimu lo ding hi. A ni masa nitakin biakpiakna-ah na piak uh sa khat peuhpeuh zong a zingsang dong zan tawntung na omsak kei ding uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Topa na Pasian un note hong piak khua khempeuhah Paisan Pawi biakpiakna na pia thei kei ding uh hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Topa na Pasian un ama min om nadingin a teelna mun bekah ni a tum khit nitak, Egypt panin na paikhiat uh hunin Paisan Pawi biakpiakna na pia ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Topa na Pasian un a teelna munah huanin na ne ding uh a, zingsang ciangin na puanbukte uhah na ciah thei ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ni guk sung silngo sawh loh anlum na ne ding uh a, a ni sagih ni-in Topa na Pasian uh a dingin a thupi kikhopna khat na nei ding uh hi. Tua ni-in na na sem kei ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “An na lak masak ni uh a kipanin nipikal sagih na simto ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tua ciangin Topa na Pasian un note thupha hong piakna tawh kizui-in na piak ding uh ahi note’ khutsung panin utthu-a piakna tawh Topa na Pasian uh tungah nipikal pawi na bawl ding uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Topa na Pasian uh mai, ama min om nadingin Topa na Pasian un a teelna munah, note a kipan na tanute le na tapate, na nasem numeite le na nasem pasalte, na khua sunga om Levi mite, peemtate, pa nei lote, le note lakah a om meigong numeite tawh na lungdam khawm ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Egypt-ah sila na hihna uh na phawk ding uh a, hih thukhamte zuih ding limtakin na ngaihsun ding uh hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Na ancilna uh le na leenggah sukna panun an na kaihkhop uh ciangin ni sagih sung buk pawi na bawl ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tua pawi sungah nang a kipan na tanute le na tapate, na nasem numeite le na nasem pasalte, Levi mite, peemtate, pa nei lote, le na khua sunga om meigong numeite tawh na lungdam khawm ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Topa in a teelna munah ni sagih sung Topa na Pasian uh tungah pawi na bawl ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh note na lungdam khawm theih nadingun na khawhsa uh le na khut uh tawh na sepna khempeuh uhah Topa na Pasian un note thupha hong pia ding hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Amah in a teelna mun, Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah pasal khempeuh kum khatin thumvei, silngo sawh loh anlum pawi, nipikal pawi, le buk pawi-ah kilaak ding uh hi. Amaute khut hawmguakin Topa’ mai-ah kilak lo ding uh hi. Topa na Pasian un note thupha hong piaknasa tawh kizui-in mi khempeuh in ama hih theih bang ciatin pia ding uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Na minam uh tawh kizui-in Topa na Pasian un note hong piakna khuate-ah thukhente le uliante na koih ding uh a, amaute in a manin mite tungah thu khen ding uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Thutang na heikhia kei ding uh a, angvan tuam na nei kei ding uh hi. Sumgolh in mipilte’ mit tawsakin thumante’ thu heikhia ahih manin sumgolh na la kei ding uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Note nungta-in Topa na Pasian un hong piak leitang na luah theih nadingun a thuman bekbekin na gamta ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Note in na bawlsa uh ahi, Topa na Pasian uh biakna tau kiangah Asherah milim dingin khuam khat peuhpeuh na phut kei ding uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Topa na Pasian un a muhdah biakna songpi na phut kei ding uh hi."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Bawng ahi a, tuu ahi zongin, poina a nei, kisapna khat peuhpeuh a om peuhmah Topa note’ Pasian’ tungah biakpiakna-in na pia kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh tua pen Topa note’ Pasian a dingin a kihhuai ahi hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Topa note’ Pasian in note hong piak khua khat peuhpeuh sungah numei ahi a, pasal ahi zongin, ama thuciamna palsatin, Topa na Pasian uh muhna-ah a sia-in a gamtatna kimu-in,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> pasian dangte’ na semin tuate bia ahi zongin, keimah in ka kham ahi ni ahi a, kha ahi a, vantung na khat peuhpeuhte’ na semin bia ahi zongin,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> no kiangah hong kigenin tua thu na zak uhleh, note in limtakin na kantel ding uh a, Israel-te sungah tua bang a kihhuai na a kigamtatna thu a om mah ahih takpi leh,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> numei ahi a, pasal ahi zongin tua banga a sia-in a gamta mi pen na khua pua uhah na paipih ding uh a, tua numei ahi a, pasal ahi zongin suang tawh na denglum ding uh hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Teci nih ahih kei leh thum bang genna tawh a si ding pa kithat ding a, teci khat bek thugenna tawh mi kithat lo ding hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> A that dingin tecite masa ding a, tua khit ciangin midang khempeuh in hih ding uh hi. Tua bangin note’ sung panin hoih lohna na siangsak ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Mi khatlekhat kithah khakna, khatlekhat thu kituhna, mi khatlekhat kisatna, note a dingin a haksalua thu khat peuhpeuh note’ khua sungah khen ding hong om leh, note kithawi-in Topa na Pasian un a teelna mun,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Levi siampite le tua huna thukhente kiangah pai-in thu na dong ding uh a, amaute in note kiangah thukhen nading hong gen ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tua ciangin Topa in a teelna mun panin note’ tungah hong gen bangun na hih ding uh hi. Amaute in note tungah hong lah bangin limtakin na hih ding uh na ngaihsun ding uh a,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> amaute in note tungah hong piak thuhilhna le note tungah hong gen uh thukhensatna tawh kizui-in na hih ding uh hi. Amaute in note tungah hong gen bang teekteekin na hih ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Topa note’ Pasian’ mai-ah nasem dingin a ding siampipa’ thu ahi a, thukhen pa’ thu ahi zongin man lohna tawh a khengvala a gamta mi peuhpeuh kithat ding hi. Tua bangin Israel-te’ sung panin hoih lohna na siangsak ding uh hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Tua hileh mi khempeuh in za-in, kihta-in, a khengvalin gamta ngam nawn lo ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Topa na Pasian un note hong piak leitangah tungin, note in tua leitang nei-in a tungah na ten uh ciangin, ‘Eite’ kimkota om minamte khempeuh mah bangin eite’ tungah kumpi khat i koih ding hi,’ na ci nuam kha ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Topa note’ Pasian in a teel mipa note’ tungah kumpi-in na koih thei takpi ding uh hi. Ahi zongin na mipihte bek uh lak panin kumpi-in mi khat na koih ding uh a, na sanggam uh ahi lo gamdang mi khat no’ tungah na koih thei kei ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Amah in ama aituam dingin sakol tampi nei lo ding hi. Topa in no kiangah, ‘Hih lampi tawnin na kilehkik ngei kei ding uh hi,’ hong ci ahih manin, amah in sakolte a lei dingin Egypt gamah mite paisak lo ding hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> A lungsim heikhia kha ding ahih manin zi la thuah lo ding a, ama a dingin ngun le kham zong nakpitakin behlap lo ding hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ama kumpi tokhom tungah a tut ciangin Levi siampite’ kep hih thukhamte ama a dingin laibu khat sungah gelh ding hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hih thukham sunga thute le hih ngeinate kemin zuihna tawh Topa a Pasian zahtak ding a theih nading, a mipihte tungah ama lungsim a kiliatsak loh nading, thupiaknate them khat zong a pelh loh nading, le Israel-te sung ahi ama kumpi gam sungah amah le a tate saupi a om theih nadingin amah in a nuntak sung tawntung tua sunga thute sim ding hi."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Siampi ahi Levi minam khempeuh in Israel-te bangin tanh ahi a, luah ahi zongin nei lo ding uh a, amaute in Topa’ tungah mei tawh kihal biaknate le a kaih ngeite uh ne ding uh hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amaute in a sanggamte uh lakah gamhluah nei lo ding uh a, amah in amaute tungah a ciam mah bangin Topa pen amaute’ luah ahi hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Bawng hitaleh tuu hitaleh biakna-in a pia mite’ tung panin siampite’ kaih dingte: Amaute in siampite’ tungah a liang le a paang nihte le a gilpi pia ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na anpal, na leenggahzu, na sathau, le na meet masak uh na tuumul uh na pia ding uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Levi minamte Topa’ na a sem tawntung dingin na minam khempeuh uh sung panin Topa na Pasian un a teel ahi hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Levi mi khat, Israel-te sung na khuapi uh khat peuhpeuh ahi ama tenna panin ama ut hun peuh ciangin Topa’ teelna munah hong pai thei ding hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tua ciangin Topa’ mai-ah nasem dingin a om a lawm Levi midangte khempeuh mah bangin Topa a Pasian’ min tawh na sem thei ding hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Amah in a gamhluah a zuakna pan a sum ngahte banah nek ding a kikimin amaute tawh tanh ngahkhawm ding hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Topa na Pasian un note hong piak leitangah na tun uh ciangin, tua minamte’ gamtatna a kihhuaite zuih ding na kisin kei ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Note lakah a tanu ahi a, a tapa ahi zongin biakna-in a zang, ai a saan, khong a khai, mailam thu a gen, ai a tawi,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bum a zang, van a kah, sikhate tawh a kiho, sikha thu a dong kuamah na om kei ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh hihte a hih mi peuhmah Topa a dingin a kihhuai ahi hi. Hih bang a kihhuai gamtatnate hangin note’ mai panin Topa na Pasian un amaute hawlkhia hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Note pen Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah paubaang loin na om ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh note in na suankhiat ding uh hih minamte in khongkhaite le aisante thu ngai uh hi. Ahih hangin note ahihleh tua bangin na gamtat ding uh Topa na Pasian un hong phal lo hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Topa na Pasian un note lak ahi na sanggamte uh lak panin note a dingin kei tawh a kibang kamsang khat hong khangsak ding hi. Note in ama thu na ngai ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Note in, ‘Si kha ding ka hih manun Topa kote’ Pasian’ aw hong zasakkik kei in. Hih a lian mei zong hong musak nawn kei in,’ ci-in na kikhop ni-un Horeb-ah Topa na Pasian uh tung pan na deih bang uh hi ding hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Amaute’ hong ngetna thuman taktak hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Amau sanggamte lak panin nang tawh a kibang kamsang khat amaute a dingin ka khangsak ding hi. Ama gen dingte ka hilh ding a, amah ka thupiak khempeuh amaute tungah a gen ding hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Amah in keima min tawh a gen ka thute a don lo mi peuhmahte kei mahmah in ka thuk ding hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ahih hangin keimah in thugen dingin thu pia lo napi-in keima min tawh thu a gen ngam kamsangpa hitaleh pasian dangte’ min tawh thu a gen pa hitaleh, tua bang mite si ding hi,’ hong ci hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Na lungsim sung uhah, ‘Topa’ gen ahi lo thu bangci theih ding ihi hiam?’ na cih uhleh,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> kamsang khat in Topa’ min tawh thu genin, tua thu pen hong tung lo ahi a, a man lo ahi zongin hong hih leh, tua thu pen Topa’ gen loh thu ahi hi. Kamsangpa in ama utthu a gen hi a, amah na kihtak ding uh kul lo hi."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Topa na Pasian un amaute’ leitang note hong piak minamte beisakin, note in amaute suankhia-in, amaute’ khuapite le innte-ah na ten uh ciangin,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Topa na Pasian un note’ neih dingin hong piak gam sungah note a dingin khuapi thum na tuamkoih ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Mi a thatkha peuhpeuh a tai theih nadingin Topa na Pasian un na neih dingun a hong piak leitang seh thumin khenin seh khat sungah khuapi khat ciat koihin a lampite na puah ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mi khat sing a phuk dingin a vengpa tawh gamlakah pai-in, sing a phuk dingin a khut tawh a hei vaanin, a heitang a ga panin kikhongin a vengpa kha-in a sih bang danin, mi khat in sawm lohpi, a beisa hunah amah tawh kigal neihna om lopi-in a vengpa a sihsak khak leh, hih khuapite khat peuhpeuhah amah tai-in a nuntakna hu thei ding hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tua bang hikeileh, amah in a beisa hunah a vengpa tawh kigal neihna nei lo ahih manin sih nading thu om lo napi-in, a hehna tawh phula nuampa in mi that khapa delhin lampi a gamlatna hangin amah pha-in a si dingin liamsak kha ding hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tua ahih ciangin, khuapi thum tuamkoih un, ci-in note thu a hong pia ka hi hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Note in Topa na Pasian uh itin, ama lampi zuih tawntungna tawh tuni-a kong gen hih thupiakna khempeuh limtakin na zuih uh a, amah in na pu na pate uh tungah a kiciam mah bangin Topa na Pasian un na gamgite uh hong keeksakin, na pu na pate uh piak dingin a ciam leitang note tungah hong piak leh, hih khuapi thum banah khuapi thum mah na behlap ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tua hikeileh Topa na Pasian un luah dingin note hong piak leitang tungah mawhbaang lo mi kithat kha ding a, tua mi thahna hanga mawhna note’ tungah hong tu ding hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Ahih hangin mi khat in a vengpa mudahin, amah pangsim a, amah satin liamsakin a sihsak a, tua mipa hih khuapi khat peuhpeuhah a tai leh,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ama khua upate in amah hong puakin hong paipih ding uh a, a sih theih nadingin phulapa tungah ap ding uh hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Note na nopsak theih nadingun amah hehpih loin, Israel-te sung panin mi that pa na beisak ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Topa na Pasian un na neih dingun hong piak leitang tungah note’ kep ding na gamhluahna sung uhah khanglui mite in a phuhsa na vengte’ gisuang na khin kei ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Mi khat in a hihkhak mawhna lian ahi a, khialhna khat peuhpeuh a gamtatna-ah ahi zongin tua mipa’ langah teci khat guak kicing lo ding a, teci nih ahih kei leh teci thum bang thugenna tawh mawhsakna kikipsak bek ding hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Elna lungsim a nei teci khat in mi khat gamta khial hi, ci-in a mawhsak leh,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> thuneite a langnih tuakin, tuahun laitak a siampite le thukhente’ mai, Topa’ mai-ah pai ding uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Thukhente in limtakin kan ding uh a, teci pa pen zuau teci hi-in, a man lopi-in a sanggampa a mawhsak ahihleh,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> a sanggampa tungah amah in hih dinga a sawm bang teekin ama tungah na hih ding uh hi. Tua bangin note sung panin gitlohna na siangsak ding uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tua hileh a omlai mite in za-in lau ding a, note lakah tua bang gitlohna bawlkik ngei nawn lo ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Amah na hehpih kei ding uh hi. Nuntakna tang ding nuntakna, mit tang ding mit, ha tang ding ha, khut tang ding khut, khe tang ding khe na hisak ding uh hi."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Na langte uh a do dingin pai-in a sakolte, a leengte, le a galkapte uh nomau-a’ sangin a tamzaw-in na muh uh hangin amaute na kihta tuan kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh Egypt gam panin note a hong paikhiatpih Topa na Pasian uh note tawh hong om hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Gal nai na tun uh ciangin siampipa a mai-ah hong pai-in mite kiangah thu genin",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> amaute kiangah, ‘Israel-te aw, za un. Tuni-in na langte uh a do dingin na nai uh hi. Na lungsim uh lausak kei un. Lau kei un, ling kei un, amaute kihta kei un.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh note tungah gualzawhna a hong pia ding, na langte uh hong dosak dingin note tawh hong kuan khawm pa pen Topa na Pasian uh ahi hi,’ ci ding hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Tua ciangin uliante in mite kiangah thu genin, ‘Inn thak lam khinin a ap nai lo kua om na hi uh hiam? Gal sungah amah si-in midang khat in a inn ap kha ding ahih manin a inn-ah ciahkik hen.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Leenggui lo kho khinin a gah a ne nai lo kua om na hi uh hiam? Gal sungah amah si-in midang khat in a gah ne kha ding ahih manin a inn-ah ciahkik hen.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> A zi dingin lawm dong khinin a la nai lo kua om na hi uh hiam? Gal sungah amah si-in midang khat in tua numei la kha ding ahih manin a inn-ah ciahkik hen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Uliante in mite kiangah thu genthuah lai-in, ‘A lau, a lungsim meidawi kua om na hi uh hiam? A lawmte meidawilawh kha ding ahih manin a inn-ah ciahkik hen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Uliante in mite kiangah thugen a man khit uh ciangin mite a makai ding kiseh ding hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “A do dingin khuapi khatpeuh na nai uh ciangin kilem nading thu gen masa un.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Note hong dawnna pen kilem nading lam hi-in note kongpi hong hon leh, tua sunga om mi khempeuh in note a dingin aana tawh na semin, na na uh hong sepsak ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ahih hangin note tawh kilemna hong bawl loin note hong do leh, note in tua khua na umcih ding uh a,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Topa na Pasian un note’ khut sungah hong piak ciangin pasal khempeuh namsau tawh na that ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ahih hangin numeite le naupangte, ganhingte, khua sunga na dang khempeuh, a kinusiate khempeuh note a dingin na la ding uh a, Topa na Pasian un note hong piak ahi na langte uh vante na tang ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hih nai-a om minamte’ khuapi ahi lo, note kiang panin a gamla khuapi khempeuh tungah tu-a bangin na hih ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ahih hangin, amau’ pasian-te a biakna uhah a hih uh a kihhuai gamtatnate khempeuh note hong hilh theih loh nading le tua bangin Topa na Pasian uh tungah na khialh theih loh nadingun, Topa na Pasian un luah dingin note’ tungah hong piak hih mite’ khuapi sungah mi khempeuh na hingkhawi kei ding uh a, Topa na Pasian un hong thupiaksa bangin Hit mite le Amor mite, Kanaan mite le Perez mite, Hiv mite le Jebus mite, a vekpi-in amaute na susiamang ding uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Khuapi khat na lak theih nadingun do-in sauveipi na umcih uh hangin hei zatna tawh a singgah kungte na susia kei ding uh hi. A gahte na ne thei ding uh a, ahih hangin a kungte na phuk kei ding uh hi. Gamlak a om singkungte, note’ sukgawp dingin na gal uh hi zenzen ahi hiam?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Nek dinga kizang lo singkung hi, ci-in na theih teng bek uh note hong do khuapi a tuk mateng umcihna-in na zat dingun na phuk thei ding uh hi."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Topa na Pasian un note’ neih dingin a hong piak leitangah mi khat kithatin gamlakah lum a, a that a kitheih kei leh,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na upate uh le na thukhente uh hong paikhia-in, a kithat mipa’ omna kiima khuapite a gamlatna teh ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tua ciangin a kithat mipa’ omna tawh a kinai pen khuapi upate in a kisin nai lo, kol a kai nai lo bawngla khat la ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tua khuapi upate in a kikho nai lo, khaici a kivawh nai lo, tuiluang a omna kuam khatah a bawngla paipihsuk ding uh a, tua kuam sungah a bawngla ngawng attan ding uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Topa na Pasian un Levi mi siampite ama na a sem ding le Topa’ min tawh thupha a pia dingin teelkhia ahih manin amaute hong pai ding uh a, kithuneihna le kitotna peuhmah amau’ thu tawh kivengsak ding hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> A kithat mipa tawh a kinai pen khuapi upate khempeuh in kuam sunga a ngawng a kitan bawngla tungah a khut uh sil ding uh a,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> amaute in teci pangin, ‘Kote in hih mipa ka that kei uh a, a kithahlam zong ka thei kei uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Topa aw, na hotkhiatsa Israel mite’ mawhna hong maisak inla, mawhna nei lo mipa a kithahna hanga mawhna na Israel mihingte hong thuaksak kei in. Mi thahna hanga mawhna pan hong maisak in,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Topa’ muhna-ah a manin na gamtat uh ciangin note lak panin mawhna nei lo mi thahna hanga mawhna tua bangin na siangsak ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Na galte uh a do dingin kuan khia-in, Topa na Pasian un note’ khut sungah amaute hong pia a, amaute salin na mat ciangun,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> salte lakah numei a melhoih khat mu-in, tua nu deihin na zi dingin na lak nop leh,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na inn-ah tua numei na ciahpih ding a, amah in a lu metin a cinte tan ding hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Amah in sal hihna puan suahkhia-in, na inn-ah om ding a, a nu le a pa’ hangin kha khat bit sung kap ding hi. Tua khit ciangin amah na luppih thei pan ding a, nang pen ama pasal hi-in, amah pen na zi hi ding hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tua ciangin, amah na deih nawn kei leh, ama utna peuhah na paisak ding hi. Ahih hangin amah daisak khin na hih manin sumin amah zuak loin, sila bangin na bawl kei ding hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Mi khat in zi nih nei a, khat itin a khat mudah a, a it leh a muhdah a zi tegel in ta nei tuakin, tapa a neih cil pen a muhdah nu tawh a neih ahihleh,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> a tapate tungah gamhluah dingin ama neihsa a hawm ciangin, a muhdah nu’ tapa cil sangin deihzawkna hangin a it nu’ tapa pen a ta cil-in bawl thei lo ding hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ama neihsa khempeuh tanh nih piakna tawh a muhdah nu’ tapa a tacil mahin sang ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh tua pa pen ama sung panin a piang masa pen ahih manin tacil hihna za pen ama a’ ahi hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Mi khat in a lungkhauh, a langpang thei, a nu’ thu ahi a, a pa’ thu ahi zongin a mang lo, a tai hangun amau’ thu a ngai lo tapa khat a neih leh,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> a nu le a pa in tua mipa manin ama khuapi upate kiang, a tenna mun kongpi-ah paipihin,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> amaute in a khuapi upate kiangah, ‘Hih ka tapa uh lungkhauhin hong langpang thei a, amah in ka thu uh hong mang lo a, an hai, zu hai bek ahi hi,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tua ciangin khuapi pasal khempeuh in suang tawh amah denglum ding uh hi. Tua bangin note’ sung panin siatna na siangsak ding uh hi. Tua hileh Israel-te khempeuh in za-in lau ding uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Mi khat in sihna thuak theih nading mawhna bawlin amah kithat a, sing tungah na khai uhleh,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> zan tawntung sing tungah ama luang na omsak kei ding uh a, a ni mahin na phum ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh khuam tungah a kikhai siluang hawm pen Pasian in muhthadah sa hi. Topa na Pasian un luah dingin note hong piak na leitang uh na ninsak kei ding uh hi."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Na mipihte’ bawngtal ahi a, a tuu ahi zongin a gammang na muh uhleh huh loin na om kei ding uh hi. A nei pa kiangah na ciahpih kik ding uh hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amah na veng nai uh hi lo a, a nei na theih kei uhleh, na inn uhah a gan ciahpihin a nei pa in hong zon mateng na kem ding uh a, hong zon ciangin na piakik ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tua bangin a la, a puan, a mangsa na muh, na mipihte’ na a mang khat peuhpeuh na hih ding uh a, huh loin na om kei ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Na mipihte’ la ahi a, a bawngtal ahi zongin lam gei-ah a kia na muh uhleh, tuate huh loin na om kei ding uh a, tuate phottohsakkikna tawh na huh ding uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Numei in pasal puan khat peuhpeuh silh lo ding a, pasal in zong numei puan silh lo ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh hih bangin a gamta peuhmah Topa na Pasian uh tungah a kihhuai ahi hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Vasabu khat, sing tung ahi a, leilakah ahi zongin, a no ahi a, a tui ahi zongin omin, a pi in a no a ompih ahi a, a op ahi zongin na muh khak zenzen uhleh, a pi pen a no tawh na la khawm kei ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> A pi na khah ding uh a, a no na la thei ding uh hi. Hih bang gamtatna pen na nopsak nading uh, sauveipi na nuntak theih nading uh ahi hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Na inn tung panun mi khat kia-in mi sihna hanga mawhna na innsung uhah na tunsak khak loh nadingun inn thak na lam uh ciangin na innkhumzang uhah tangban na khung ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Na leenggui lo uhah khaici nam nih na vawh kei ding uh hi. Vawh le-uh cin na vawh uh an le na leenggui lo uhah a piang khempeuh a nin suak ding hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Bawngtal khat le la khat tawh lo na khokhawm kei ding uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Samul le khau a kigankhawm puan na silh kei ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Na puanza uh kiu lite tungah puanmongteep na bawl ding uh hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Mi khat in zi la-in, amah a luppih khit ciangin amah mudahin,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> a zumhuai gamtatna tawh tua nu mawhsakin, ‘Keimah in hih numei ka la a, amah tawh ka lupkhop ciangin ama sungah nungakna lim ka mu kei hi,’ cihna tawh tua nu tungah minsia a tut leh,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> tua numei’ nu le a pa in a tanu uh’ nungakna lim a kilatna puan lakhia-in upate kiang kongpi-ah paipih ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Numei’ pa in upate kiangah, ‘Hih mipa tungah a zi dingin ka tanu ka pia a, amah in deih nawn lo a,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Na tanu’ sungah nungakna lim ka mu kei hi,” cihna tawh a zumhuai-in amah mawhsak hi. Ahi zongin hihte pen ka tanu’ nungakna a kilatna limte ahi hi,’ ci-in a puan lak ding hi. Amaute in khua upate mai-ah a puan phah ding uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tua ciangin tua khua upate in tua mipa la-in sat ding uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Amaute in ngun shekel zakhat liausak ding uh a, a numei’ pa’ tungah tuate pia ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amah in Israel nungak tungah minsia tun hi. Tua ciangin a numei pen ama zi mah hi ding a, a nuntak laiteng tua nu ma thei lo ding hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Ahih hangin a mawhsakna thumanin, numei sungah nungakna lim a kimuh kei takpi leh,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> amaute in a pa’ inn kongah a numei paipih ding uh a, ama khuapi pasalte in suang tawh amah denglum ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amah in a pa’ inn sungah paktat gamtatna tawh Israel sungah haina tun hi. Tua bangin note’ lak panin siatna na siangsak ding uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Mi khat, midang khat’ zi tawh a lumkhawm a kimuh leh, numei tawh a lum pa le a numei, a nih tuakun kithat ding hi. Tua bangin Israel sung panin siatna na siangsak ding uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “A kidongsa nungak khat om a, mi khat in khuapi sungah tua nu tuakin amah tawh a lupkhop leh,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> tua khuapi kongpi-ah amau tegel na paipih ding uh a, a numei khuapi sungah a om hinapi-in mi’ huhna ngen dingin a kiko lohna hang le, tua pasal in a vengpa’ zi a va suksakna hangin, suang tawh a nihun na denglum ding uh hi. Tua bangin note’ lak panin siatna na siangsak ding uh hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Ahih hangin mi khat in a kidongsa nungak khat gamlakah tuakin, mipa in tua nu buanin a luppih leh, tua numei tawh a lum mipa bek kithat ding hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> A numei’ tungah bangmah na hih kei ding uh hi. Numei’ tungah sih nading mawhna om lo hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh hih thu pen mi khat in a vengpa do-in a thah tawh kibang hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hih mipa in gamlakah numei hih ahih manin, a kidongsa numei in huhna ngen dingin a kiko hangin amah a hon ding kuamah om lo hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Mi khat in a kidong nai lo nungak khat tuakin, tua numei buanin luppih a, amau tegel a kimuh leh,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> numei tawh a lum pa in nungak’ pa tungah ngun shekel sawmnga pia ding a, tua numei ama zi hi ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amah in a numei va su khin hi. A nuntak laiteng tua numei ma thei lo ding hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> “Mi khat in a pa’ zidangte tenpih lo ding a, a pa-a’ ahi numei tawh mawh lo ding hi."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “A ciltang a kitam ahih kei leh, a pasal na a cing lo mipa Topa a’ ding kikhopna sungah lut lo ding hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Zawlta peuhmah, Topa a’ ding kikhopna sungah lut lo ding hi. A suan a khak khang sawmna dong nangawnin Topa a’ ding kikhopna sungah tua bang mi kuamah lut thei lo ding hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Ammon mite ahi a, Moab mite ahi zongin Topa a’ ding kikhopna sungah lut thei lo ding uh hi. A khang sawmna dong nangawnun Topa a’ ding kikhopna sungah lut thei ngei peuhmah lo ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Egypt panin na paikhiat lai-un lampi-ah anletui tawh amaute in note hong dawn lo uh a, note hong samsia dingin Mesopotamia gam Pethor khua panin Beor’ tapa Balaam cial uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ahih hangin Topa na Pasian un Balaam’ thu ngai lo hi. Topa na Pasian un note hong it ahih manin, Topa na Pasian un samsiatna pen note a dingin thupha-in hong heisakzaw hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Amaute’ nopsak nading ahi a, a daupai nading uh ahi zongin na khantawnun na hanciam kei ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Edom mite khatpeuh na mudah kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute na sanggam uh ahi hi. Egypt mi khatpeuh na mudah kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amau’ gamah peemta na hi ngei uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Amaute’ sung pana piang a khang thumna mite a kipan Topa a’ ding kikhopna sungah lut thei ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Na galte uh a do dingin kuanin giahphual ah na om uh ciangin, siatna nam khempeuh panin nomau na kikem ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Note lakah, zan sungin ama tungah thupiang hangin a siang lo mi a om leh giahphual pualamah amah paikhia ding a, giahphual sungah hong pai lo ding hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ahih hangin nitak ciangin amahmah tui sungah kisil ding a, ni a tum ciangin giahphual sungah hong paithei ding hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Giahphual pua-ah awnghawh nading mun khat na nei ding uh hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na galhiamte uh banah tulzum khat na nei ding uh a, awng na hawh khit uh ciangin tua tawh lei to-in, na ek uh na vuk ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh note hong hon ding le note’ mai-a na galte uh a hong pia dingin Topa na Pasian uh na giahphual laizang uhah hong pai hi. Tua ahih ciangin note lakah a kilawm lo nate a muh loh nading le note kiang panin amah a paikhiat loh nadingin na giahphual uh siangtho ding hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “A topa’ kiang panin no kiangah a hong tai sila, a topa kiang mahah na apkik kei ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na khuapite uh lak panin ama teelna mun, ama lungkim penna, note lakah note tawh amah hong teng ding a, amah na nengniam kei ding uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Israel ta numeite biakinn sunga a paktat pawlin om lo ding uh a, Israel tapate zong a paktat pawlin om lo ding uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A paktat nu a kiguaihna sum ahi a, a paktat pa a kiguaihna sum ahi zongin thuciamna khat peuhpeuh piakna-in Topa note’ Pasian’ inn sungah na paipih kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh hih tegel pen Topa note’ Pasian’ tungah a kihhuai ahi hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Na sanggampa tungah sumgum hitaleh, ankhing hitaleh, a meet ngaihsutna-in na khat peuhpeuh leitawi na pia kei ding uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Gamdang mi tungah a meetin leitawi na pia thei ding uh a, ahih hangin na sanggampa tungah a meetin leitawi na pia kei ding uh hi. Hihte pen a luah dingin na tumna uh gam sungah Topa na Pasian un na sepna khempeuh uhah thupha hong piak theih nading ahi hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Topa note’ Pasian’ tungah thuciamna na bawl ciangun na ciamna uh tungsak loin na ommawk kei ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian un hong kal teekteek ding a, note tungah khialhna hong hi ding hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ahih hangin thuciamna bawl ding pan na kikep uhleh note’ sungah khialhna om lo ding hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na kam uh tawh na ciamsa uh thu pen Topa note’ Pasian’ tungah nomau utthu-a na ciam uh ahih manin na kam uh panin a gingkhia peuhmah na tunsak ding uh na ngaihsun ding uh hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Na vengpa’ leenggui lo-ah na pai uh ciangin na ut zahzah uh na kham dong uh leenggah na ne thei ding uh a, ahih hangin na van sung uhah na guang kei ding uh hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na vengpa’ ankung ding laite lakah na pai uh ciangin na khut uh tawh a vuite na zut thei ding uh a, ahih hangin phiaukawi tawh na vengpa’ ankung ding laite na at kei ding uh hi."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Mi khat in zi la-in a tenpih ciangin, tua nu tungah kilawm lohna a om manin numei in a pasal’ mitah maipha mu lo a, amah in makna lai gelhin ama tungah pia-in ama inn panin sawlkhia a, a pasal’ inn panin amah kihem khia-in,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> amah pai-in midang khat’ zi va suak a,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> a pasal nunung in amah deih lo leuleu a, makna lai gelhin a numei’ khut sungah koih a, a inn panin tua nu sawlkhia-in, tua ahih kei leh zi dinga a la a pasal nunung a sih leh,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> tua numei a hawlkhia a pasal masa in, tua nu a kinitsak khit ciangin a zi dingin lakik thei nawn lo ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh tua pen Topa’ mai-ah kihhuaina hi a, Topa note’ Pasian un luah dingin hong piak leitang tungah mawhna na tunpih kei ding uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Mi khat in zi a neih tungin galkapte tawh kuankhia lo ding a, nasep khat peuhpeuh zong kisawl lo ding hi. A laksa a zi tawh a lungdam khawm dingin inn-ah kum khat sung maang ding hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Kuamah in an gawina ahi a, an gawina suangpek a tungnung ahi zongin khapna-in la lo ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh khapna-in nuntakna a la suak ding hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Mi khat in Israel mi a sanggamte khat gu-in, amah in sila bangin a bawl ahi a, a zuak ahi zongin a kimuh leh, tua guta pa kithat ding hi. Tua bangin note’ lak panin siatna na siangsak ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Phaknatna hong tun ciangin Levi siampite in hong gen bangin na gamtat ding uh ngaihsun un. Amaute ka thupiakna bangin na gamtatna dingun na kingaihsun ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Egypt panin na paikhiat lai-un lampi-ah Topa na Pasian un Miriam’ tungah a hihna phawk un.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Na vengte uh tungah na khat peuhpeuh leitawi na piak uh ciangin ama hong khapna a la dingin a inn-ah pai kei un.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A pualamah na ding ding uh a, leitawi na piakna mipa in nang kiangah a na khap hong paipih ding hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Amah mizawng ahihleh ama hong khap puan na zantaamsak kei ding uh a,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ni a tum ciangin, a puanza silhin nang thupha hong piak theihna dingin tua hong na khap ama kiangah na piakik ding uh hi. Tua pen Topa note’ Pasian’ mai-ah note a dingin thumanna hi ding hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “A zawng a cimawh a kicial nasempa, na sanggamte khat ahi a, na gam sung na khuapite sunga om peemta khat peuhpeuh ahi zongin, na nengniam kei ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> A sep ni-in ama thaman, nitum ma-in na pia ding uh hi (bang hang hiam cih leh amah zawng a, tua bek a lungsimah om hi). Tua hikeileh Topa’ tungah amah in hong khia ding a, note na mawh ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Tate’ tangin pate kithat lo ding a, pate’ tangin zong tate kithat lo ding hi. Mi khempeuh ama khialhna hang bekin kithat ding hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Peemta’ thu ahi a, pa nei lo mi’ thu ahi zongin tuate a’ ding thutang na heisak kei ding uh a, meigong numei’ puan zong khapna-in na laksak kei ding uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Egypt-ah sila na hihna uh le Topa note’ Pasian in tua lai panin hong hotkhiatna na phawk ding uh hi. Tua ahih manin hih banga na gamtat nading uh thu kong pia hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Na lo-ah an la-in lo lai-ah anlom na mangngilh uh ciangin a tawm dingin na paikik kei ding uh hi. Tuate pen peemta, pa nei lo, le meigong numeite a’ ding ahi hi. Hih pen Topa note’ Pasian in na khut uh tawh na sepna khempeuh uhah note thupha hong piak theih nading ahi hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na oliv kungte uh na sat uh ciangin a hiangte na sat kikkik kei ding uh hi. Tuate pen peemta, pa nei lo, le meigong numeite a’ ding ahi hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na leenggui lo panun leenggah na kaihkhop uh ciangin a sang na nung khop kik kei ding uh hi. Tuate pen peemta, pa nei lo, le meigong numeite a’ ding ahi hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Egypt gamah sila na hihna uh na phawk ding uh hi. Tua ahih manin hih bangin na gamtat nadingun thu kong pia hi."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Mite kikalah thu kineihna om a, thukhen zumah amaute pai-in, thukhente in amau’ thu khensakin, a dikpa khahin a mawh pa lelsak a,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> a mawh pa satna thuak dinga kilawm ahihleh, thukhen pa in amah lumsuksakin a khialhna zahin ama muhin satsak ding hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sat sawmli kipia thei ding a, ahih hangin tua val hi lo ding hi. Tua hikeileh, hih sangin a tamvei zaw mi khat in sat lai leh note’ muhna-ah na sanggampa uh a kineubawl suak ding hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Bawng in an a cil laitakin a muk na tuam kei ding uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Sanggam pasalte teng khawmin, tuate khat si-in tapa a neih kei le, a sipa’ zi pen innkuan pualam khualmi tawh kiteng lo ding hi. A pasal’ sanggampa in luppihin a zi dingin amah la ding a, ama tungah pasal’ sanggampa’ nasep sem ding hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ama min Israel tungah a maiman’ loh nadingin tua nu in a neih masak a tapa pen a sisa a pasal’ ta-in kiseh ding hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mipa in a sanggampa’ zi a laknop kei leh, upate kiang kongpi-ah a sanggampa’ zi pai ding a, ‘Ka pasal’ sanggampa in a sanggampa’ min Israel sungah a zop ding ut lo a, pasal’ sanggampa’ nasep kei tungah hong sem nuam lo hi,’ ci ding hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tua ciangin mipa’ khuapi upate in amah samin thu genpih ding uh hi. Amah in, ‘Tua nu ka la nuam kei hi,’ a cih teitei leh,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> upate’ omin a sanggampa’ zi ama kiangah paito-in a khe panin a khedap kaihkhiatsakin a maitang cilphih ding hi. Tua ciangin tua nu in, ‘A sanggampa’ innkuan a zomto lo mipa hih bangin kibawl ta hen,’ cikhia ding hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Israel mite lakah ama innkuan pen, ‘A khedap a kikaih khiatsak mipa’ innkuan,’ kici ding hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Mi khatlekhat a kilai ciangin, a satpa’ kiang panin a pasal a honkhia dingin a khat pa’ zi hong pai a, a khutin a selsimte a matsak leh,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> tua nu’ khut na sattansak ding uh a, amah na hehpih kei ding uh hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Na ipsung uhah tawisuang nam nih, a lian le a neu, na neikhawm kei ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na innsung uhah tehna nam nih, a lian le a neu, na neikhawm kei ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tawisuang a cing a man na nei ding uh a, tehna a cing a man na nei ding uh hi. Topa note’ Pasian in hong piak leitangah na khan uh a sau theih nading ahi hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh tua bangin gamta-in, a thuman lote khempeuh, Topa note’ Pasian’ tungah a kihhuai ahi hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Egypt panin nong paikhiat lai-un lampi-ah Amalek mite in note hong bawlna,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> note gimin lungkhamin na om laitakun lampi-ah a hong simna, le note’ nungah a nunung khempeuh hong thahna uh phawk un; amaute in Pasian kihta lo uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tua ahih ciangin Topa note’ Pasian in note’ neih dingin gamh-in hong piak leitang tungah, Topa na Pasian un na kiim uha na galte khempeuh panun tawlngakna hong piak ciangin, mun khempeuh panin Amalek mite a kiphawkna na phiatkhiat ding uh na mangngilh kei ding uh hi."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Topa na Pasian un luah dingin a hong piak leitangah va pai-in, tua leitang luahin a tungah na ten uh ciangin,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Topa na Pasian un a hong piak leitang pana piang gah khempeuh panin a gah masa pawlkhat la-in lawh khat sungah na koih ding uh a, ama min na omsak nadingun Topa na Pasian un a teelna munah na pai ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tua hun laitakin na a sem siampipa kiangah pai-in ama kiangah, ‘Topa in kote piak dingin ka pu ka pate uh tungah a ciam leitangah ka tun khitna uh tuni-in Topa na Pasian kiangah kong ko uh hi,’ na ci ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Tua ciangin siampipa in note’ khut panin a lawh hong saang ding a, Topa note’ Pasian biakna tau mai-ah koih ding hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Topa note’ Pasian mai-ah note in, ‘A vak kawikawi kote’ pupi pen Aram mi hi a, amah Egypt-ah paisukin tua munah a peem lai-in mi tawmno ahi hi. Tua lai-ah amah a lian, a thahat, tampi a pha minam khat a suak hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Egypt-te in kote hong ngong bawlin hong gimsak a, kote sal bangin hong bawl uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tua ciangin ka pu ka pate uh Pasian ahi Topa Pasian’ tungah ka kiko uh a, Topa in kote’ aw hong za-in, ka gimnate uh, ka sepnate uh le hong netniamnate uh a mu hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Topa in a vangliatna le a thahatna, launa lianpi, lim le na lamdangte tawh Egypt panin kote hong paikhiatpih hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Amah in hih mun hong tunpihin, bawngnawi le khuaizu tui bangin a luanna gam hih leitang ko tungah hong pia hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tua ahih ciangin en in, Topa, nangmah in kote nong piaksa leitang panin a gah a min masa kong paipih uh hi,’ na ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin Topa note’ Pasian’ mai-ah na koihsuk ding uh a, Topa note’ Pasian’ mai-ah na bia ding uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Topa note’ Pasian in note le na innkuanpihte uh tungah hong piak na a hoih khempeuhte hangin note le Levi mite le note lakah a om peemtate na lungdam khawm ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Sawm-ah-khat piak kum ahi, a kum thumna kumin, amaute in na khuapite uh sungah an ne-in, gilvahin a om theih nadingun Levi mite, peemtate, pa nei lote, le meigong numeite tungah na piak uh, na khawhsa uh sawm-ah-khat na piak khit uh ciangin,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Topa note’ Pasian’ mai-ah, ‘Ka innsung panin a siangtho dingteng ka tuamkoih khin hi. Tua tham loin kei nong sawlna bangin na thupiaknate khempeuh tawh kizui-in Levi mite, peemtate, pa nei lote, le meigong numeite tungah ka pia khin hi. Hih tungtangah na thupiakna khat zong ka khial kei a, ka mangngilh zong om lo hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Dahin ka kah sungin zong sawm-ah-khat ka ne kei a, ka nit sungin zong ka khenkhia kei a, misite tungah zong ka pia kei hi. Topa ka Pasian’ thu ka mang a, kei nong thupiakna khempeuh bangin ka hih khin hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Vantung, nangma omna a siangtho panin hong ensuk inla, kote’ pulepate tungah bawngnawi le khuaizu tui bangin a luanna gam na ciam mah bangin, nangma mi Israel-te le na hong piaksa leitang thupha hong pia in,’ na ci ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Tuni-in Topa na Pasian un hih thukhamte le ngeina kipte na zuih ding uh note tungah thu hong pia hi. Tua ahih ciangin na lungsim khempeuh uh le na nuntakna khempeuh uh tawh na hih ding uh limtakin na ngaihsun ding uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tuni-in, Topa pen note’ Pasian ahihna le note in ama lampite tawnin, ama thukhamte le ama thupiaknate le ama ngeina kipte zui-in, ama thu na man’ ding uh na gen khin uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tuni-in Topa in note pen amah in note tungah hong ciamsa bangin ama neih ding mi na hihna uh, le note in ama thupiaknate khempeuh na zuih nading uh,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ama bawlsa minam dangte khempeuh sangin phatna le minthanna le pahtawina a lianzaw a ngahin hong koih nading, le ama gensa mah bangin Topa note’ Pasian a dingin a siangtho mi na hih nading uh hong gen khin hi,” a ci hi."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tu-in Moses le Israel upate in mite thu pia-in, “Tuni-a kong gen uh thupiakna khempeuh na zui ding uh hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Topa na Pasian un note hong piak leitangah pai dingin Jordan na kantan ni-un suangtumpite na phut ding uh a, buan tawh na zut ding uh hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na pu na pate uh Pasian ahi Topa in note tungah hong ciam mah bangin bawngnawi le khuaizu tui bangin a luanna leitang, Topa na Pasian un note hong piakna gamah a lut dingin na galkah uh ciangin tua suangte tungah hih thute na gelh ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Jordan na galkah khit uh ciangin Ebal Mual tungah tuni-a kong thupiakna uh tawh kizui-in hih suangte na phut ding uh a, buan tawh tua suangte na zut ding uh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tua lai-ah Topa na Pasian uh a dingin suang kibawl biakna tau khat na bawl ding uh a, tuate tungah sik tawh a kibawl nazatte na liik kei ding uh hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Topa na Pasian uh a dingin a kiseek lo suangtumte tawh biakna tau na bawl ding uh a, tua biakna tau tungah Topa na Pasian uh a dingin meihal biaknate na pia ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tua ciangin thunuama biaknate na pia ding uh a, tua lai munah ne-in, Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah na lungdam ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hih thute khempeuh tua suangte tungah a kitel takin na gelh ding uh hi,” a ci uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tua ciangin Moses le Levi siampite in Israel-te khempeuh tungah, “Israel-te aw, gamdai unla ngai un: Tuni-in Topa note’ Pasian’ mi na suak uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Tua ahih ciangin Topa note’ Pasian’ thu mangin, tuni-a kong gen uh ama thupiaknate le ama thukhamte na zui ding uh hi,” a ci uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Moses in tua ni mahin mite thuhilhin,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Jordan na galkah khit uh ciangin mite thupha a pia dingin Gerizim Mual tungah a ding ding minamte: Simeon, Levi, Judah, Issakhar, Josef, le Benjamin ahi hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ebal Mual tungah hamsia a pia dingin a ding ding minamte: Reuben, Gad, Asher, Zebulun, Dan, le Naftali ahi hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Levi mite in awging lianpi tawh Israel mite khempeuh tungah hih bangin ci ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “‘Topa a dingin a kihhuai ahi, khutsiampa’ khut tawh a kibawl, a kiseek ahi a, a kisung ahi zongin milim bawlin, mun simthamah a koih mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in dawngin, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “‘A nu ahi a, a pa ahi zongin a zahtak lo mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “‘A vengpa’ gisuang a botkhia mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “‘Mittaw pa lam a lakkhial mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “‘Peemta, pa nei lo, le meigong numeite a’ ding thutang a heikhiatsak mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “‘Amah in a pa’ tungah maizumna tun ahih manin, a pa’ zidang tawh a lumkhawm mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “‘Ganhing khat peuhpeuh tawh nulepa mawhna a bawl mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “‘A nu’ tanu, a pa’ tanu, ahih kei leh a sanggamnu tawh a lumkhawm mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “‘A sungnu tawh a lumkhawm mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “‘A vengpa a thatsim mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “‘Mawhna nei lopa thah nadingin sumgolh a la mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “‘Hih thute zuihna tawh hih thu a kipsak lo mipa in gimna ngah ta hen,’ ci ding uh hi. Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, ‘Amen,’ ci ding uh hi."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Note in Topa na Pasian uh thu mangin, tuni-a kong gen ama thupiakna khempeuh limtakin na zuih uhleh Topa na Pasian un leitung minam dangte khempeuh sangin a lianzaw-in note hong bawl ding hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Topa na Pasian uh thu na man’ uhleh hih thuphate khempeuh note tungah hong tung ding hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Khuapi sungah thupha ngah mi na hi ding uh a, lote-ah zong thupha ngah mi mah na hi ding uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Note’ sung pana piangte, le na leitang uh pana piangte, le na ganhing uh pana piang, na bawngte uh pungin na tuuhonte uh tungah thupha om ding hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Na seengte uh le na annel mekna kuangte uhah thupha om ding hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Na sepna khempeuh uhah thupha na ngah ding uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Topa in, note’ langah hong pang na galte uh na mai uhah lelhna thuaksak ding hi. Amaute lampi khat tawnin hong kuan ding uh a, note’ mai panin lam sagih tawnin taikeek ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Topa in note’ ansal tung le na hihna khempeuh uhah thupha hong puak ding hi. Topa na Pasian un note hong piakna leitangah amah in note tungah thupha hong pia ding hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Note in Topa na Pasian uh hong thupiaknate zui-in ama lampi na tot uhleh amah in note tungah hong ciamsa bangin ama a dingin a siangtho mi dingin Topa in note hong kipsak ding hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Topa in note hong sapna thu midang khempeuh in thei ding uh a, amaute in note hong kihta ding uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Note piak dingin na pu na pate uh tungah Topa in a ciamsa gam sungah note’ sung pana piangte, na gan khawi pan uha piangte, le na leitang pan uha piangte-ah Topa in note nakpitakin hong hausak ding hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Note’ leitangah ama hunin guah a zusak ding le na sepna khempeuh uh thupha a pia dingin Topa in a na hoih kholna vantung note hong hon ding hi. Note in minam tampite tungah leitawi na pia ding uh a, ahih hangin note in leitawi na la kei ding uh hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Note in tuni-a kong thugente limtakin zuihna tawh Topa na Pasian uh thupiaknate mangin, tuni-a no kong thupiakna kammalte panin, pasian dangte’ na semin a bia dingin na pial kei nak-uhleh, Topa in a makai-in note hong bawl ding a, mi’ nung zui-in hong bawl lo ding hi. Tunglam bekah na kah ding uh a, na nuaikiat ngei kei ding uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Ahih hangin note in Topa na Pasian uh thu mang loin, tuni-a kong gen ama thupiaknate le ama thukhamte khempeuh limtakin na zuih kei uhleh, hih samsiatna khempeuh note tungah hong tung ding a, note hong ban ding hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Khuapi sungah hong kisamsia ding a, lo-ah zong hong kisamsia ding hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Na lawhte uh le na annel mekna kuangte un zong samsiatna ngah ding hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Note’ sung pana piangte le na leitang uh pana piangte, na bawngte uh le na tuuhon note uh in zong samsiatna ngah ding hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Na sep na bawlna khempeuh uhah hamsia na ngah ding uh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Note in Topa na nusiat uh a, na gamtatsiat uhleh, note sia-in na sihmang khit matengun Topa in note tungah samsiatna, buaina, cihmawhnate hong tungsak ding hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> A luah dingin na lutna uh leitang panin note hong beisak matengin note lakah pulnatna a tun nadingin Topa in bawl ding hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Topa in pulnatna le cisa natna, meima nasia le a sa mahmah keutumna, huihpi’ mutgawpna le a nom tawh note hong vatgawp ding a, note na sih matengun tuate na thuak ding uh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na lu tung uha om vantungte pen sumngo bangin sanin guah zu lo ding a, na nuai uha om leitung pen sik bangin sak ding hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Topa in na gam sung uha guahte tang dingin leivui le sehnel hong zusak ding a, note na sih matengun vantung panin note tungah tuate hong kiasuk ding hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Topa in na galte uh mai-ah note hong guallelsak ding hi. Amaute a do dingin lam khatah na kuan khawm ding uh a, amau’ mai-ah lam sagihin na taikeek ding uh hi. Leitung kumpi gamte khempeuh’ muhna-ah note a cikzethuai na hi ding uh hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Note’ luanghawmte pen huih lak a leeng vasate khempeuh le leitung a ganhingte khempeuh’ an hi ding a, tuate a bengkhia ding mihing om lo ding hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Topa in note na damkik theih loh nading uh Egypt meimatumte le meima daite, meima lipneite le cithak tawh note hong vatgawp ding hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Topa in haina, mittawtna, le lungsim buaina tawh note hong vatgawp ding hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Mittawte in khuamial lakah khua a zawt bangin sunin khua na zawt ding uh a, na hihnate uhah na maavang kei ding uh hi. Note hong kinengniamin na tate uh hong kisut niloh ding a, note hong huh ding kuamah om lo ding hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> “Zi dingin lawm khat na dong ding uh a, midang khat in na luppih ding hi. Inn na lam ding uh a, tua sungah na teng kei ding uh hi. Leenggui lo na zuan ding uh a, a gah na ne kha kei ding uh hi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na muh tangpi-un na bawngtal uh kigo ding a, a sa na ne kha kei ding uh hi. Note’ mai panin na la uh hong kingawh laksak ding a, note kiangah hong kipia kik nawn lo ding hi. Na tuute uh na galte uh tungah kipia ding a, note hong huh ding kuamah om lo ding hi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na tapate uh le na tanute uh midang tungah kipia ding a, amaute ngai-in sun nilohin na mit un enin na mit uh gim ding hi. Tuate pen nomau’ tha tawh na dalzawh ding uh hi lo ding hi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na theih nai loh uh minam khat in na leitang panun a piangte le na nasepsa khempeuh uh ne tum ding a, note hong kinengniamin hong kisugawp tawntung lel ding hi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Tua ahih ciangin na mit un a muh ding nate in note hong hehsak mahmah ding hi.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Topa in note na kidamsakkik theih loh ding uh a nasia mahmah meimatumte tawh na khukte uh le na khete uh meimasak gawpin, na khenuai panun na luzang dong uhah na thuak ding uh hi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Note le na pu na pate un a theih ngei loh minam khat kiangah Topa in note le note tungah na koih uh na kumpipa uh hong tunpih ding a, tua lai-ah singlesuang tawh a kibawl pasian dangte’ na na sem ding uh hi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Topa in note hong paikhiatpihna mite lakah a cikzethuai, paunak, le gentehna na suak ding uh hi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> “Khaici tampi lo-ah na tuh ding uh a, ahi zongin tawmno bek na khawm ding uh hi; bang hang hiam cih leh kauphe in nemang ding hi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Note in leenggah lo zuanin na puah ding uh a, ahih hangin leenggahzu dawn loin, leenggah zong na ne kei ding uh hi; bang hang hiam cih leh lung in tuate ne ding hi.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na gam sung khempeuh uhah oliv kung na nei ding uh a, ahih hangin a thau tawh note na kizut kei ding uh hi; bang hang hiam cih leh na oliv gahte uh pulh ding hi.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Tanute le tapate na nei ding uh a, ahih hangin amaute pen nomau a’ hi lo ding uh hi; bang hang hiam cih leh amaute galmat suak ding uh hi.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na singte khempeuh uh le, na leitang panun a piang khempeuh kauphete in tang ding uh hi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> “Note lakah a om peemtate lian semsem ding uh a, note na neu semsem ding uh hi.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Amaute in note’ tungah leitawi hong pia ding uh a, note in amaute tungah leitawi na pia kei ding uh hi. Amaute a makai hi-in, note a nungzui na hi ding uh hi.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> “Amah in note hong piak thupiaknate le thukhamte zui loin, Topa na Pasian uh thu mang lo na hih manun, note na sih matengun hih samsiatnate khempeuh note’ tungah hong tungin, note hong delhin hong pha ding uh hi.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Note le na suanlekhakte uh tungah a tawntungin tuate pen lim le nalamdang hi ding hi.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Hih a tampi nate khempeuh om napi-in note in lungdamna le lungsim kipahna tawh Topa note’ Pasian’ na sem lo na hih manun,",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Topa in note’ langah a hong sawl ding na galte uh’ na, gilkialna le dangtakna, pum guakin omna, le na khempeuh kitangsapna tawh, na sem ding uh hi. Na galte un note hong suksiat matengin note’ ngawngah sik hakkol hong thuah ding uh hi.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Topa in a gamlapi leimong panin muvanlai leeng bangin a manlang, amau’ pau na theih loh uh minam, thukhualna a nei lo minam, khangham mite a zahtak lo, khangno mite tungah maipha zong a lak tuan lo minam khat, note’ langkhatah hong paipih ding a,",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> note na sih matengun amaute in na ganhon note uh le na leitang panun a piang gahte hong neksak ding uh hi. Amaute in note hong beisak matengun note a dingin an, leenggahzu, ahih kei leh sathau, na ganhingte uh ahih kei leh na tuuhon note uh zong hong nusiat lo ding uh hi.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Na gam sung uha a om na muan uh, a sang a muanhuai na kulhpite uh a cip khit dong matengin note’ khuapite khempeuh sungah amaute in note hong umcih ding uh hi. Topa na Pasian un note hong piaksa na gam sung khempeuh uhah a om na khuapite khempeuh sung uhah note hong umcih ding uh hi.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> “Na galte un hong umcihna le hong lungkhamsak nading ahi na lungkham hun sung uhah Topa na Pasian un note a hong piaksa, na sung panun a piang na tanute uh le na tapate uh’ sate na ne ding uh hi.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Note lakah a ngeksuak, a cithei pen mipa in a sanggampa, a it a zi, le amah tawh a om a tate a nunung pen’ tungah an pia nuam lo ding hi.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Na khuapite khempeuh sung uhah hong umcihna le na galte un note hong lungkhamsak nading hun sungah bangmah kinei nawn lo ding ahih manin ama nek a tate’ sate kuamah in midang hawm nuam lo ding hi.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Note lakah a om a ngeksuak, a cithei pen numei, amah ngekin a ci neel lua ahih manin a khenuai tawh lei sik ding a ngaihsun ngei vet lo nu in a it a pasal, a tanute le a tapate a dingin ama sung panin a piang a tate le ama sung panin a paikhia a nau-nungzuite phal lo ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh hong umcihna le na galte un na khuapite uhah note hong lungkhamsak nading lungkhamna sungah bangmah neih lohna hangin amah in tuate nesim ding hi.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> “Hih a minthang, a zahtakhuai min, Topa na Pasian uh na kihtak theih nadingun hih laibu sunga kigelh hih thute limtakin zuih ding na ngaihsut kei uhleh,",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Topa in note le na suan na khakte uh tungah nasia-in sauvei a om gimna, gimna a tuan diak, le a nasia, nat saute hong tungsak ding hi.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Amah in note’ kihtak Egypt natnate note’ tungah hong tungsakkik ding a, note’ tungah tuate kilawi lo ding hi.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Note na siat matengun hih thukham laibu sungah a kiciamteh lo natna le gimna khempeuh zong Topa in no tungah hong tungsak ding hi.",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Note, vantung aksite zahin a tam na hihna sung uhah tawmno bek na pha ding uh hi; bang hang hiam cih leh Topa na Pasian uh thu na mang kei uh hi.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Topa in note tungah a hong bawlna le note tampi hong phaksakna-ah nuam a sak mah bangin, note tungah siatna tunsakna le note suksiatna-ah zong Topa in nuamsa ding a, a luah dingin na lutna uh leitang panin note hong kilakhia ding hi.",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> “Topa in leimong khat panin mong khat, mi khempeuhte lakah note hong thehthang ding hi. Tua lai-ah note le na pu na pate un a theih nai loh singlesuang tawh a kibawl pasian dangte’ na na sem ding uh hi.",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Hih minamte lakah oltak a nuntakna na mu kei ding uh a, kiptaka na om nading uh gam na nei kei ding uh hi. Topa in tua lai-ah lungsim linna, mit gimna, le nuntak tha beina hong pia ding a,",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> na nuntakna uh lunghimawhin na om tawntung ding uh hi. Sun le zanin na lau ngitnget ding uh a, nuntak lungmuanna na nei kei ding uh hi.",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> Na lungsim un a kihtak launa le na mit un a muh ding nate’ hangin, zingsangin, ‘Nitak hileh!’ na ci ding uh a, nitakin, ‘Zingsang hileh!’ na ci ding uh hi.",
			"68": "<sup>68</sup> Note na zin kik ngei nawn kei ding uh hi, ci-in kong ciam khualzinna, Egypt gamah teembaw tawh Topa in note hong paipih kik ding hi. Tua lai-ah sila numei le sila pasal dingin na galte uh tungah na kizuak ding uh a, ahih hangin kuamah in note hong lei lo ding hi,” a ci hi."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hihte pen, Horeb-ah amaute tawh thuciamna a bawlsa banah, Israel mite tawh Moab gamah thuciamna a bawl dingin Topa in Moses a sawl, a thuciamna kammalte ahi hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Moses in Israel-te khempeuh samin amaute kiangah, “Egypt gam sung note’ mit muhah, Topa in Faro’ tung le ama nasemte khempeuh le ama gam khempeuhah a bawlna,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> note’ mit in a muhsa ze-etna lianpite, limte, tua nalamdang liante khempeuh na thei khin uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ahih hangin tuni dongin Topa in note’ tungah a thu na tel nading uh lungsim hitaleh, na muh nading uh mit hitaleh, na zak nading uh bil hitaleh hong pia nai lo hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kum sawmli sung sehnel gamah note hong makaih khin hi. Note’ tung panin na puante uh sia nai lo a, na khe panun zong na khedapte uh sia nai lo hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Topa pen na Pasian uh ahihna na theih nadingun nek ding anlum, le dawn ding leenggahzu ahi a, khamtheih zu ahi zongin na ne nai kei uh a, ahi zongin na kisapna teng uh hong pia hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hih mun na tun uh ciangin Heshbon kumpipa Sihon le Bashan kumpipa Og, eite a do dingin hong kuankhia uh a, ahih hangin amaute i zo hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Amaute’ leitang i la a, Reuben mite, Gad mite, le Manasseh minam alangte tungah luah dingin i pia hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tua ahih ciangin na hihna khempeuh uhah na daupai theih nadingun hih thuciamna kammalte khempeuh limtakin na zuih ding uh na ngaihsun ding uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Topa na Pasian un tuni-in note tawh a bawl, Topa na Pasian uh thuciamna sungah na lut theih nadingun, tuni-in amah in ama mi dingin note hong kipsak theih nading, le note’ tungah hong ciamna le na pu na pate uh Abraham, Isaac, le Jakob tungah a kiciamna bangin, amah, note’ Pasian ahih theih nadingin, na minam lutangte uh, na upate uh, na uliante uh, Israel mi pasal khempeuh, na taneute uh, na zite uh, na giahphual uhah a om peemtate, na sing uh hong tomsakin na tui uh a hong tawisakte a kipan note khempeuh, tuni-in Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah na ding uh hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hih kiciamna note bek tawh a bawl hi lo a,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> tuni-in eite tawh Topa i Pasian’ mai-ah a ding mite tawh a bawl mah bangin tuni-in eite tawh a om nai lo i suan i khakte tawh zong a bawl ahi hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Egypt gamah i tenna le note in na nawk uh minamte lakah i paina na thei uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> A muhdahhuai amau’ na, singlesuang a kibawl, ngunlekham a kibawl, amaute’ lakah a om a milimte uh na mu khin uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Note lakah numei ahi a, pasal ahi a, innkuan ahi a, minam khat ahi zongin, tua minamte’ pasian a bia dingin Topa i Pasian kiang panin tuni-in a lungsim a heikhia a omkhak ding kidawm un. Tua hikeileh note lakah gu a nei gah kha a gah singkung hong bang ding a, hih kiciamna kammalte za napi-in a lungsimah amah thupha kipia tawmin, ‘Ka lungsim khauhna tawh ka gamta zongin ka suakta veve ding hi,’ a ci hong om kha ding hi. Hih in mihoih le misia, a kibangin phiatkhiatna hong suaksak ding hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Topa in amah maisak lo ding a, Topa’ hehna le hazatna meikhu bangin tua mipa’ langkhatah khuzaw-in, hih laibu sunga kigelh samsiatnate ama tungah tu ding a, Topa in a mun khempeuh panin ama min phiat ding hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Topa in hih thukham laibu sunga a kigelh thuciam samsiatnate khempeuh tawh kizui-in gimna a thuak dingin Israel minamte khempeuh lak panin amah tengkhia ding hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Hong khanglai ding, note’ nungah hong piang na tate uh, le a gamla gam panin a hong pai gamdang mite in, tua gam’ gim ngahna le Topa in a natsak cinatnate a muh uh ciangin,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ‘A gambup pen kaat le ci, le nin a kangtum, khai kituh lo, bangmah po lo, lopa zong a po zawh lohna mun Sodom le Gomorrah, Admah le Zeboiim bangin a kilawnthal gawp, a hehna le a sinsona tawh Topa’ lotgawpte tawh kibang hi,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Minam khempeuhte in, ‘Bang hangin Topa in hih bangin hih gam bawl ahi hiam? Hih hehna lian, bang a cihnopna ahi hiam?’ ci takpi ding uh hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Tua ciangin mite in, ‘Amah in Egypt gam panin a paikhiatpih lai-in amaute tawh a bawl, a pu a pate uh Pasian ahi Topa’ thuciamna amaute in nusia-in,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> a theih nai loh uh pasian-te le amah in amaute tungah a piak loh pasian dangte’ na va semin a biakna hang uh ahi hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Tua ahih ciangin a mite tungah Topa heh mahmah a, hih laibu sunga om samsiatnate khempeuh hih leitungah tungsak hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Topa in hehna, sinsona, lungham mahmahna tawh a leitang panun amaute zunglot a, tuni-a i muh bangin amaute gam dangah hawlkhia hi,’ ci ding uh hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Topa i Pasian in hong lahkhiat loh thusim om a, ahih hangin hih thukham sunga om thute khempeuh i zuih theih nadingin hong lakkhia a, eite le i suan i khakte’ zuih tawntung ding ahi hi."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Note’ mai-ah ka koih, na teel ding thu thupha le samsiatna, hih nate khempeuh note tungah hong tungin, Topa in note hong hawlkhiatna minamte lakah hih thute phawk kikin,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Topa note’ Pasian’ kiangah note le na suan na khakte uh paikikin, na lungsim khempeuh uh le na nuntakna khempeuh uh tawh tuni-a kong gen ama thute na man’ uh ciangin,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Topa na Pasian un note na ngei uh hong bangsakkikin, note tungah hehpihna hong nei ding a, Topa na Pasian un note hong thehthangna mi khempeuhte lak panin note hong kaikhawm kik ding hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A kihawlkhia na mite uh van mong pekah a om leh zong, Topa na Pasian un tua lai panin note hong khawmin, tua lai panin amah in hong paipih ding hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Note in na neih theih nadingun, na pu na pate uh neih leitangah, Topa na Pasian un hong paipih ding a, na pu na pate uh sangin a citheizaw a tamzaw-in note hong bawl ding hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Note in na lungsim khempeuh uh le na nuntakna khempeuh uh tawh Topa na Pasian uh itin na hintheih nadingun, Topa na Pasian un note le na suanlekhakte uh tungah thu man’ nopna lungsim hong guan ding hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Topa na Pasian un hih samsiatnate khempeuh, no hong bawlsia na galte uh le na langte uh tungah tungsak ding hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Note in Topa’ thu mangkikin, tuni-a kong gen ama thupiaknate khempeuh na zui ding uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Note in hih thukham laibu sunga kigelh ama thupiaknate le ama thukhamte zui-in, Topa na Pasian uh thu na man’ uh a, na lungsim khempeuh uh le na nuntakna khempeuh uh tawh Topa na Pasian uh lamah na kihei uhleh, Topa na Pasian un na sepna khempeuh uh, note’ suanlekhakte, na ganhingte uh panin a piangte, le na leitang panun a piang khempeuhah nakpitakin hong daupaisak ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh na pu na pate uh tungah amah a lungkim mah bangin note tungah Topa hong lungkim kik ding a, note hong daupaisak ding hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Bang hang hiam cih leh tuni-a kong gen hih thupiakna pen note a dingin a haksa lua hi lo a, na zuihlah ding uh zong hi lo hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Note in, ‘Eite in a thu za-in i sep theih nadingin kua in vantungah eite a dingin hong paisakin hong laksak ding ahi hiam?’ na cih theih nadingun vantung a om hi lo hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Note in, ‘Eite in a thu za-in i sep theih nadingin kua in tuipi galkhatah hong paisakin hong laksak ding ahi hiam?’ na cih theihna dingun tuipi gal-a om zong hi lo hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> A thu, hong nai mahmah hi. Note in na hih theih nadingun na kamsung uh le na lungsim sung uhah om hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Tuni-in na teel dingun note’ mai-ah nuntakna le a hoih na, sihna le siatna ka koih khinzo hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Topa na Pasian uh itna, ama lampite totna, ama thupiaknate le ama thukhamte le ama ngeina kipte zuihna tawh, tuni-a no tungah kong gen ahi Topa na Pasian uh thupiaknate na man’ uhleh, note nungta-in tampi na pha ding uh a, a luah dingin note na lutna uh leitang tungah Topa na Pasian un note thupha hong pia ding hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ahih hangin na lungsim uh kihei-in, note in amah zui loin, pasian dangte a bia ding le a na a sem dingin note na kiheikhiat uhleh,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> tuni-in note tungah hih thu kong genkhol hi: Note na si ding uh a, Jordan kantanin note a lut ding le a nei dingin na paina uh leitang tungah sauvei na nungta kei ding uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tuni-in note’ langkhatah teci a pang dingin vantung le leitung ka sam a, note’ mai-ah na teel dingun nuntakna le sihna, thupha le samsiatna ka koih hi. Tua ahih ciangin note le na suanlekhakte uh na hintheih nadingun nuntakna teel unla,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Topa na Pasian uh itin, ama thu mangin, amah beel un; bang hang hiam cih leh Topa in na pu na pate uh Abraham, Isaac, le Jakob tungah piak dingin a kiciamsa leitangah note na tentheih nadingun tua pen note-a’ dingin nuntakna le khansauna ahi hi,” a ci hi."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tua ciangin Moses in Israel-te khempeuh tungah a thugen zomlai hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amah in amaute kiangah, “Tuni-in kei kum za le kum sawmnih ka pha ta a, keima ut bangin ka gamtangzo nawn kei hi. Topa in kei kiangah, ‘Hih Jordan galkhatah na pai kei ding hi,’ hong cizo hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Topa na Pasian mahmah uh note’ mai-ah hong galkah ding hi. Note’ mai-ah hih minamte amah in susia ding a, note in amaute na suankhia ding uh hi. Topa’ gensa bangin note’ mai-ah Joshua hong galkah ding hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Topa in amaute a suksiat lai-in, Amor kumpi Sihon le Og tung le amau’ leitang tungah a bawl bangin amaute tungah bawl ding hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Topa in note tungah amaute hong pia ding a, note kong piak thupiaknate khempeuh tawh kizui-in amaute tungah na bawl ding uh hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Thahat unla, hang un. Lau kei unla, amaute kihta kei un. Bang hang hiam cih leh note tawh hong pai pa pen Topa na Pasian uh ahi hi. Note hong cimawhsak lo ding a, hong nusia lo ding hi,” a ci hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tua ciangin Moses in Joshua samin, Israel-te khempeuh muhin ama kiangah, “Thahat inla hang in. Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute tungah piak dingin Topa in amau’ pute pate tungah a ciamsa leitangah hih mite tawh na pai ding a, nangmah in tua leitang amaute na ngahsak ding hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mai-ah a pai pa pen Topa ahi hi. Amah in nang hong ompih ding a, nang hong cimawhsak loin, zong hong nusia lo ding hi. Lau kei inla, lungkia kei in,” a ci hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Moses in hih Thukham gelhin Topa’ Thuciamna Singkuang a pua Levi mi siampite le upate khempeuh tungah a pia hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Moses in amaute thu pia-in, “Kum sagih a cin sim, a kisehsa suahtaksakna hun, buk pawi hunin,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> amah in a teelna mun Topa na Pasian uh mai-ah a kilak dingin Israel-te khempeuh a pai uh ciangin, amau’ zakin Israel-te khempeuh mai-ah hih thukham na sim ding uh hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Jordan galkhatah a luah dingin na paina uh gamah na nuntak laitengun amaute in a thu za-in Topa na Pasian uh zahtak ding a theih nading, le hih thukham thute khempeuh limtakin a sep theih nading, le hih thu a thei nai lo amau’ tate in Topa na Pasian uh zahtak ding a theih nadingun, numei, pasal, le naupangte, le na khuapite uh sunga om peemtate, mi khempeuh khawm un,” a ci hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tua ciangin Topa in Moses kiangah, “En in, na sih ding hun hong nai ta hi. Joshua sam inla, amah ka sawl theih nadingin kikhopna buk sungah hong om un,” a ci hi. Tua ciangin Moses le Joshua pai-in kikhopna buk sungah va om uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tua ciangin meii khuam omna puanbuk sungah Topa kilang hi. Meii khuam, puanbuk kong gei-ah a ding hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tua ciangin Topa in Moses kiangah, “En in, na pu na pate kiang a zuan ding na hita hi. Nang na om nawn loh ciangin hih mite pen na paina uh mite lakah a gam sung pasian-te uh tawh paktat ding uh a, amaute in kei hong nusia-in amaute tawh ka bawl ka thuciamna uh siasak ding uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tua hun ciangin amaute tungah ka sin so-in, amaute nusia-in ka mai ka seel ding a, amaute beimang ding uh hi. Tua ni ciangin amaute in, ‘Eite’ lakah i Pasian a om loh manin hih siatnate i tungah hong tung hi lo ahi hiam?’ a cih theih nadingun amaute tungah siatna le gimna tampi tung ding hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Amaute, pasian dangte lamah kihei uh ahih manin amau’ gamtatnasa siatnate khempeuh hangin tua hun ciangin ka mai ka seel taktak ding hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin hih lai gelh inla, Israel mite hilh in. Hih la, kei a dingin Israel mite’ langkhatah teci a suah theih nadingin amaute tungah hilh in.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh a pu a pate uh tungah piak dinga ka kiciamna, bawngnawi le khuaizu tui bangin a luanna gamah amaute tunpih khinin, amaute in ne-in khamin a thau khit uh ciangin, pasian dangte a bia dingin kihei-in kei hong simmawhin ka thuciamna siasak ding uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Siatna le haksatnate amaute tungah a tun ciangin hih la, teci-in amaute’ langkhatah pang ding hi (bang hang hiam cih leh a suanlekhakte un mangngilh lo ding uh hi); bang hang hiam cih leh piak dingin ka kiciam leitangah amaute ka paipih ma-in, amau’ vaihawm kholh a ngimnate uh ka thei hi,” a ci hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Tua ahih ciangin tua ni mahin Moses in hih la gelh a, Israel mite a hilh hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Tua ciangin Topa in Nun’ tapa Joshua sawlin, “Thahat inla hang in; bang hang hiam cih leh amaute piak dingin ka kiciam leitang tungah Israel mite na paipih ding a, nang tawh kong om ding hi,” a ci hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Moses in a bei dongin hih Thukham kammalte laibu sungah a gelh a man ciangin,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Moses in Topa’ Thuciamna Singkuang a pua Levi mite thu pia a,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Hih Thukham laibu la unla, note’ langkhatah teci dingin a om theih nadingin Topa na Pasian uh Thuciamna Singkuang gei-ah koih un.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh a lehdo mite le a lungkhauh thei mite na hihna uh ka thei hi. En un, note tawh kei a nungta khawm laipi mahin, tuni-in Topa na lehdo khin uh hi. Ka sih khit ciangin bangzah takin lehdozaw lai ding na hi uh hiam!",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hih thute amaute’ bilah genin, amau’ langkhatah teci a pang dingin vantung le leitung ka sap theih nadingin na minam upate uh le na uliante khempeuh uh kei kiangah hong khawm un.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh ka sih khit ciangin note siatgamtatin, note kong sawlna lampi panin na pial taktak ding lam uh ka thei hi. Note’ sepna tawh amah hehsakin, Topa’ muhna-ah a sia gamta ding na hih manun, hong pai ding hunte-ah, note’ tungah gimna hong tung ding hi,” a ci hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Tua ciangin hih la malte a bei dongin Israel a kikhawm khempeuhte’ zakin Moses in gen a,"
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Vantungte aw, ngai un, thu kong gen ding hi. Ka thugente leitung in za hen.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka thuhilhte guahmal bangin zu-in, ka thugente daitui bangin kia hen la, lo ngeek tunga guah phin leh ankung tunga guahzu bang tahen.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Topa’ min ka phat ding hi. Eite’ Pasian a liatna gen un!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Eite’ belh Topa, a nasepna kicing a, ama sepna khempeuh thumanna ahi hi. Thumanna nei-in, mawhna a nei lo Pasian hi a, amah thutangin thuman hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ama tungah amaute gamtat sia uh a, amaute’ sitbaanna hangin ama tate hi nawn lo uh hi. Amaute pen a lampial, a lungsim kawi khang mite ahi uh hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> A hai, ngaihsutna nei lo mite aw, tua bangin Topa thuk ding na hi uh hiam? Amah pen, note a hong piangsak, note hong bawlin a hong kipsak, na pa uh hi lo ahi hiam?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “A beisa hunte phawk unla, khang tampi hunte ngaihsun un. Na pate uh dong le-uh cin, hong hilh ding uh a, na upate uh dong le-uh cin hong gen ding uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sang Pen pa in minam dangte tungah amau’ gamh pia a, mihingte a ten nading mun a seh ciangin vantungmi a phazah tawh a kizui-in mite’ gamgi a phut hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ahi zongin Topa’ tanh pen ama mite hi a, Jakob’ suante pen a kipia ama luah ahi hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Amah in sehnel gam, huihpi nunna gam sungah amaute mu hi. Amah in amaute kawi-in kem a, ama mitnauta bangin amaute kem hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A bu a vil, a note tungah a kha a zap, a khate zakin a note a man, a kha tawh a note a pua muvanlai bangin",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Topa bek mah in amaute makaih a, amaute kiangah gamdang pasian om lo hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Amah in leitung a sangna-ah amaute tuangsak a, amaute in gamlak pana piangte a ne uh hi. Suangpi panin amaute khuaizu hupsakin, meisuang tawh a kibang suang panin sathau a nesak hi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bawnghon panin bawngnawi thaukhal, tuuhon panin tuunawi, tuunote le tuutalte’ thau tawh, Bashan bawnghonte le keelte, mangbuh hoihpente tawh leenggahtui san na dawn uh hi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Israel mite thau mahmah uh a, a lehdo thei mi suak uh hi. Note thau-in lianpi pha-in, na zol uh hi. Tua ciangin amaute a bawl Pasian amaute in nusia-in, amau a Honkhia pa thusim lo uh hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Amaute pen pasian dangte tawh ama hazat theih nadingin gamta uh a, a kihhuai gamtatnate tawh amaute in amah hehsak uh hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Amaute in pasian ahi lo dawite, amau’ theih ngei loh pasian-te, hong suak nunung pasian thakte, na pu na pate un a theih ngei loh pasian-te’ tungah biakna a pia uh hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Note a hong Honkhia pa na phawk kei uh a, note a hong suaksak Pasian na mangngilh uh hi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Topa in tua thu thei a, a tapate le a tanute in amah hehsak uh ahih manin tua ama tate a nolh hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Amah in, ‘Amaute’ kiang panin ka mai ka seel ding a, amaute’ thumong bang hong hi hiam, ka en ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute a lampial khang mite hi a, cihtakna a nei lo tate ahi uh hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Amaute in pasian a hilote tawh ka hazat nading hong bawl uh a, a milimte uh tawh kei hong hehsak uh hi. Tua ahih ciangin mi-a a gen taak lo mite tawh amaute’ hazat theih nading ka bawl ding a, a hai mahmah minam khat tawh amaute ka hehsak ding hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh ka hehna in mei tawhkuang a, Leinuaite’ gamdong a kuang hi. Leitung le a tunga piangte kangtum a, mualte’ bulpite kuangsak hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “‘Amaute’ tungah siatna ka khol ding a, amaute’ tungah ka thaltangte ka zang ding hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Gilkialin amaute si ding uh a, a sa mahmah meikuang le gunei natna in amaute netum ding hi. Keimah in amaute a pet dingin ha hiam a nei gamsate amaute a tu dingin gu a nei gulte ka sawl ding hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Namsau in gamlakah amaute susia-in, inn sungah launa lianpi om ding a, tangval le nungak, naungek nawi nete, samkangte tawh susia khawm ding hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Keimah in, “Amaute gamlapi-ah ka thehthang ding a, mite lakah amaute a kiphawkna ka beisak ding hi,” ka ci thei ding hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Amau’ langte in ngaihsun khialin, amaute in, “Eite i gualzo hi. Topa in hihte khempeuh bawl lo hi,” hong ci kha ding uh ahih manin galte’ hong phin ding ka lau hi,’ a ci hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute, ngaihsutna a nei lo minam hi a, amaute’ sungah thu theihtelna om lo hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Amaute a pil hileh, hih thu theitel ding uh a, amau’ thu tawpna mu ding uh!",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Amau a Honkhia pa in amaute zuakin, Topa in amaute piakhia kei leh bangci-in mi khat in mi tulkhat delh mangin, mi nih in mi tul sawm taisakzo ding ahi hiam?",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh i galte’ pasian eite’ Pasian bang hi lo a, i galte’ thungetna a mawkna ahi hi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Amaute, Sodom le Gomorrah bangin siahuai uh a, gu nei-in a kha leenggah a gah leenggui tawh kibang uh hi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Amau’ leenggahzu pen gulpi gu le a gupha gul gunei gu tawh kibang hi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Hihte kei kiangah kikholin, ka vankoihna sungah kisiincip hi lo ahi hiam?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Phulakna le thukkikna kei a’ hi a, a hun ciangin amaute puk ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amau’ gim ngah hun ding hong naita a, amau’ siat nading hong tung pah hi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute’ vang a beina le sila le sila a hilote a beina a muh ciangin Topa in a mite’ dikna kilangsak ding a, ama nasemte tungah hehpihna nei ding hi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Tua ciangin amah in, ‘Amau’ pasian-te, a bukna uh suangpi,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> amaute’ biakpiakna thau ne-in, leenggahzu tawh a biakna uh a dawnte koi-ah om ahi hiam? Amaute thosakin note kihuhsak unla, amaute, na kidalna uh hisak un!",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> ‘Tu-in thei un, keimah a kici pa pen kei ka hi a, kei simloh pasian dang kuamah om lo hi. Ka that a, ka nungtasak hi. Ka liamsak a, ka damsak hi. Ka khutsung pan a honkhiazo kuamah om lo hi.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh vantung lamah ka khut laamto-in ka kiciam a, a nungta tawntung ka hih mah bangin,",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> a tee ka namsau taatin, thu ka khen ciangin, ka galte tungah phu ka la ding a, kei hong mudahte ka thukkik ding hi.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ka thaltangte si ka tawksak ding a, ka namsau in mi that ding hi. a kithatte le a kimante, kei hong langpangte, sugawp ding hi,’ a ci hi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Topa’ mite phat un, no minam dangte aw; bang hang hiam cih leh amah in a nasemte’ phu la a, alangte thuk-in, ama mite’ gam adingin kilemna a bawl hi,” a ci hi.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Tua ciangin Moses hong pai-in, mite’ zakin amah le Nun’ tapa Joshua in hih la malte khempeuh a sut uh hi.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Moses in Israel-te khempeuh tungah hih thute a gen a man ciangin",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> amaute kiangah, “Hih thu khempeuh limtakin zui unla, na tate un a zuih dingin na hilh theih nadingun tuni-a note tungah kong gen thu khempeuh na lungsim uhah koih un.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh hih pen note a dingin a thuneu hi loin note’ nuntakna hi a, a luah dingin Jordan galkhat na paina uh gam sungah hih thu tawh sauveipi na hing ding uh hi,” a ci hi.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Tua ni mahmahin Topa in Moses kiangah,",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> “Jerikho gallam, Moab gam sungah a om Nebo Mual, hih Abarim mualtungah kahto in. A neih dingun Israel mite tungah ka piak Kanaan gam gal et in.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Hor Mual tungah na sanggampa Aaron si-in a mite kiangah a kigawm bangin, na kahtohna mualtungah si inla, na mite kiangah pai-in kigawm in.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Zin gam, Kadesh khua gei-a Meribah tui phual, Israel mite lakah keimah nong upna na siasak a, Israel mite lakah a siangtho-in kei nong zahtak kei hi.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Tua ahih manin na mai-ah a om gam na gal muh tei ding a, ahih hangin Israel mite ka piak gam sungah nang na pai kei ding hi,” a ci hi."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hih pen, Pasian’ mi Moses in ama sih ma-in Israel mite thupha a piakna ahi hi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amah in, “Sinai panin Topa hong pai a, Sinai panin eite a’ ding hong suakkhia hi. Paran Mual panin hong taangkhia a, a taklam khutah meikuang tawi-in, mi siangtho tul sawmte kiang panin a hong pai hi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hi taktak hi; amah in a mite it a, ama tungah a ki-ap mi khempeuh a khut sungah om hi. Tua ahih ciangin amaute in na kalsuanna hong zui uh a, nang tung panin lamlahna ngah uh hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Jakob mihonte’ neih dingin Moses in kote tungah ngeina khat hong pia hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Mite’ makaite kikhawmin, Israel minamte khempeuh a kikaihkhop ciangin, ama mi Israel-te lakah Topa, kumpi a suak hi,” a ci hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Reuben minamte’ thu gen a, “Reuben nungta-in si kei hen la, ama mite zong mi tawm hi kei ta hen,” a ci hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tua ciangin Judah minamte’ thu genin, “Topa aw, Judah’ aw ngai inla, a mite kiangah amah paipih in. Na khutte tawh ama a’ ding do inla, a galte’ dona-ah a huhpa hi in,” a ci hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tua ciangin Levi minamte’ thu genin, “Levi tungah na Thummim pia inla, na midik pa tungah na Urim pia in. Massah ah na ze-et mipa, Meribah tuite-ah na kitotpih pa ahi hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> A nu le a pa sangin nangmah hong thupi ngaihsutzaw uh a, ‘Amaute ka thupi sim kei hi,’ a ci pa ahi hi. Amah in a sanggamte paaikhia-in, a tate don lo hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh Levi minamte in na thu hong mangin, na thuciamna zui uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Amaute in na ngeina kipte Jakob suante hilhin, na thukhamte Israel-te hilh ding uh hi. Amaute in na mai-ah paknamtui hong koihin, na biakna tau tungah meihal biakna bup hong koih ding uh hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Topa aw, ama nate tungah thupha pia inla, a khut tawh a sepnate saang in. A galte’ kawng sutan inla, a ding kikzo nawn lo dingin amah a mudahte sugawp in,” a ci hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Benjamin minamte’ thu genin, “Topa in a it mipa ama kiangah nuam takin om hi. Amah in sun tawntung kemin, amaute lakah om hi,” a ci hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Josef minamte’ thu genin, “Topa in ama leitang, tung lamah a om vantung letsong hoihpente, le nuai-a om a thuknate tawh,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ni hanga gah a hoihpente, le kha hanga piang a hoihpente tawh,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> tanglai mualte tunga piang a hoih a limci pente le tawntung mualte’ hauhna tawh,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> leitung le a tunga om letsong hoihpente le sawlbawk lakah a tengpa’ maipha tawh thupha pia tahen. Hihte khempeuh, Josef tungah tung hen la, a sanggamte lakah ulian ahi mipa’ lu tungah tung tahen.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> A tacil, bawngtal bangin thahat a, a kite, gamsial kite tawh kibang hi. Amah in tuate tawh mite nawt ding a, leimong dongah amaute khempeuh phul ding hi. Efraim mi tul sawmte tua bang hi a, Manasseh minam tul tampite zong tua bangmah ahi hi,” a ci hi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Zebulun minamte’ thu genin, “Zebulun aw, na paikhiatna-ah lungdam in. Issakhar aw, na puanbukte sungah lungdam in.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Amaute in a mual uhah mite sam ding uh a, amaute in tua lai-ah biakpiakna mante pia ding uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute in tuipi tung le sehnel sungah na manpha kiseelte ngah uh hi,” a ci hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Gad minamte’ thu genin, “Gad a lianin a bawlpa in thupha ngah ta hen! Gad in humpinelkai bangin buk khikhe a, amah in a baan le a luzang, a balkham hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Amah in lei hoihpenna mun ama a dingin teel hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh a ukpa’ tanh kikoihcingsak hi. Mi makaite’ ngahte mah amah zong kingahsak a, amah in Israel-te tawh Topa’ thupiakna le thuman khennate a sem hi,” a ci hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Dan minamte’ thu genin, “Dan pen Bashan panin a diangkhia humpinelkai no ahi hi,” a ci hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Naftali minamte thu genin, “O Naftali, maipha tawh nuam a sa, Topa’ thupha tawh a kidim, bualtuite le leitaw lam a nei pa,” a ci hi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Asher minamte thu genin, “Asher in tapa dangte sangin thupha ngahzaw tahen. A sanggamte’ pahtak hi hen la, a gam sungah oliv thau kidim tahen.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na khuapite, sik le sumngo tawh kidal ding a, na nuntak laiteng na thahatna tua bang hi ding hi,” a ci hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Israel aw, nangmah huh dingin vantungah a tuang a liatna tawh vanpi-ah a om, Pasian tawh a kibang kuamah dang om lo hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Tawntung Pasian pen nangma omna hi a, nangmah huh dingin tawntung khutte a om hi. Amah in na mai-ah galte nawtkhia-in, ‘Susia un,’ ci hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Tua ahih ciangin Israel mite lungmuangin om ding uh hi. Jakob suante bek an le leenggahzu gamah om hi. Hi taktak hi, a vantungte in daitui hong khiatsuk hi. Israel aw, mi nuamsa na hi hi. Nang hong kihuhna lum le na gualzawhna lum le na gualzawhna namsau ahi Topa in nang banga a hotkhiat mi kua om ahi hiam?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na galte in hong mai-etin, na kiangah hong pai ding uh a, amaute na tuancil ding hi,” a ci hi."
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tua ciangin Moab zanglei panin Jerikho gal Nebo Mual, Pisgah dawnah Moses paito hi. Tua ciangin Topa in gam khempeuh, Gilead gam pan Dan ciang dong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Naftali gam khempeuh, Efraim le Manasseh gam, Judah gam khempeuh Nitumna Tuipi dong,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Negeb gam, le nisuh kung khuapi kuam a kici Jerikho panin Zoar ciang dong a kikhung zanglei a lak hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tua ciangin Topa in ama kiangah, “Hih gam, Abraham, Isaac, le Jakob tungah kiciamin, ‘Na suanlekhakte uh tungah ka pia ding hi,’ ka cih leitang ahi hi. Na mit tawh nang kong musak khin a, ahih hangin tua lai-ah nang na pai kei ding hi,” a ci hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tua ahih ciangin Topa’ thugenna bangin Topa’ nasem Moses pen Moab gamah si a,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bethpeor galkhat, Moab gam kuamah amah kiphum hi. Ahih hangin tuhun dongin a kiphumna mun kuamah in thei lo hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Moses a sihin kum za le kum sawmnih pha hi. A mit maang lo a, a tha ngeina zong kiam lo hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Moab zanglei-ah Israel mite ni sawmthum sung Moses hangin a kah khit uh ciangin Moses hangin kahna le thumna a veng ta hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tua ciangin Moses in, ama tungah a khut nga khin ahih manin Nun tapa Joshua lungsim pilna tawh a kidim hi. Tua ahih ciangin Israel mite in ama thu mangin, Topa in Moses a thupiaksa bangin a gamta uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Israel mite sungah Moses bangin Topa in maitang kimu-in a theih kamsang dang kuamah om lo hi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Egypt gam sungah Faro le a nasemte le a gam khempeuhah a hih dingin Topa in ama tungah a piak limte le na lamdangte khempeuh a nei kuamah dang om lo hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Israel-te khempeuh muhna-ah Moses in a hih a lian vangliatna le a lauhuaite khempeuh a hih thei, amah tawh a kibang kuamah dang om lo hi."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;